WEBVTT

00:06.333 --> 00:08.333
<i>[whimsical music playing]</i>

00:40.125 --> 00:42.125
<i>[dramatic instrumental music playing]</i>

01:52.000 --> 01:54.125
<i>[man] Everything's going</i>
<i>to be fine, darling.</i>

02:16.791 --> 02:18.791
<i>Madam, it's so wonderful to see you.</i>

02:19.208 --> 02:20.833
<i>Welcome home from the hospital.</i>

02:21.541 --> 02:23.250
<i>Jenny, this is Mrs. Cordoza.</i>

02:23.333 --> 02:26.208
<i>Yes. Thank you.</i>

02:27.041 --> 02:28.875
<i>I'll show you to your room, madam.</i>

02:40.125 --> 02:42.291
<i>[Cordoza] Everything is just</i>
<i>as you like it.</i>

02:45.333 --> 02:47.583
<i>[unlocks]</i>

03:22.416 --> 03:23.791
<i>[ambulance sirens wailing]</i>

03:36.166 --> 03:38.250
<i>[dramatic instrumental music playing]</i>

04:02.708 --> 04:04.458
<i>I'm so happy to have you back home.</i>

04:29.708 --> 04:30.833
<i>Good night, dear Jenny.</i>

04:36.041 --> 04:37.041
<i>Good night, Lawrence.</i>

04:41.958 --> 04:42.791
<i>Larry.</i>

04:45.583 --> 04:46.500
<i>You call me Larry.</i>

04:47.000 --> 04:47.833
<i>Larry.</i>

05:15.708 --> 05:16.541
<i>[groans]</i>

05:17.708 --> 05:18.666
<i>[groans]</i>

05:18.750 --> 05:19.708
<i>[man whispers] Hey.</i>

05:21.125 --> 05:21.958
<i>[groans]</i>

05:23.250 --> 05:24.583
<i>Hey. [groans]</i>

05:25.625 --> 05:27.791
<i>Oh hey! Um…</i>

05:28.875 --> 05:31.458
<i>Fancy seeing you here. [yawns]</i>

05:31.541 --> 05:32.458
<i>Uh…</i>

05:33.041 --> 05:33.875
<i>I actually…</i>

05:34.625 --> 05:37.291
<i>I have to sort of</i>
<i>start getting ready for work, so…</i>

05:37.375 --> 05:40.000
<i>I might have to ask you to, um…</i>

05:41.583 --> 05:42.416
<i>-to, uh…</i>
<i>-Um.</i>

05:42.875 --> 05:45.916
<i>-If you don't mind.</i>
<i>-This is actually my flat. So…</i>

05:47.083 --> 05:48.833
<i>Oh shit. Um…</i>

05:49.583 --> 05:52.416
<i>Well, in that case, at ease, </i>monsieur.

05:52.500 --> 05:54.916
<i>-[man groans]</i>
<i>-</i>No problemo.

05:55.000 --> 05:56.500
<i>Love to see you again.</i>

05:56.625 --> 05:57.583
<i>As in, um…</i>

05:58.625 --> 06:00.416
<i>I had a really great time last night.</i>

06:00.500 --> 06:03.875
<i>Um, well, the thing is, Rob, I'm just--</i>

06:03.958 --> 06:04.875
<i>My name's not Rob.</i>

06:06.208 --> 06:07.041
<i>Um…</i>

06:08.000 --> 06:09.625
<i>-Andrew.</i>
<i>-Andrew.</i>

06:10.291 --> 06:11.291
<i>Um…</i>

06:11.375 --> 06:18.000
<i>I actually… I just sort of came out</i>
<i>of quite a straight-up soul-destroying…</i>

06:18.083 --> 06:19.750
<i>So, thank you.</i>

06:19.833 --> 06:23.291
<i>-I'm just saying I can give you my number.</i>
<i>-Or you could not.</i>

06:23.375 --> 06:27.291
<i>And we could avoid the whole me</i>
<i>feeling guilty and never calling you back.</i>

06:27.375 --> 06:29.916
<i>You feeling dejected,</i>
<i>never hearing from me again.</i>

06:30.000 --> 06:30.916
<i>I feel so used.</i>

06:31.000 --> 06:33.375
<i>Well, you know what, Rob?</i>
<i>Welcome to my world.</i>

06:33.458 --> 06:35.416
<i>-Name's not Rob.</i>
<i>-Andrew.</i>

06:35.500 --> 06:36.750
<i>[softly] Fuck, sorry.</i>

06:38.500 --> 06:40.875
<i>Well, Andrew,</i>

06:40.958 --> 06:45.583
<i>it's been very nice meeting you,</i>
<i>and you have a lovely day.</i>

06:45.666 --> 06:48.083
<i>["Cherry Flavoured Stomachache"</i>
<i>by Haim playing]</i>

06:49.958 --> 06:51.125
<i>-[man] Ellie?</i>
<i>-Yes.</i>

06:51.541 --> 06:54.875
<i>♪ Tried to withdraw a guilty plea ♪</i>

06:58.458 --> 07:02.000
<i>♪ Damn!</i>
<i>You ain't gonna pin this one on me ♪</i>

07:06.166 --> 07:09.416
<i>♪ One thing's for sure</i>
<i>I'm not sleeping here tonight ♪</i>

07:13.291 --> 07:17.083
<i>♪ And I'm not interested</i>
<i>In what you think is bad ♪</i>

07:20.750 --> 07:23.958
<i>♪ But I get so lonely</i>
<i>I can't relate to anyone ♪</i>

07:24.666 --> 07:29.791
<i>♪ And my heart is crying out</i>
<i>I'm on my knees ♪</i>

07:29.875 --> 07:33.125
<i>♪ I'm begging you please</i>… <i>♪</i>

07:33.208 --> 07:34.125
<i>How's it going?</i>

07:37.208 --> 07:38.791
<i>[woman 1] Staff meeting in five.</i>

07:38.875 --> 07:39.708
<i>[Ellie] Nick?</i>

07:41.375 --> 07:42.208
<i>Nick!</i>

07:42.291 --> 07:45.625
<i>I'm not talking to you, Ellie, because</i>
<i>that only involves me losing my shit.</i>

07:45.708 --> 07:46.833
<i>What did I do?</i>

07:46.916 --> 07:49.541
<i>I get it. You've had a shit year, Ellie,</i>

07:49.625 --> 07:52.291
<i>but it is just not cool</i>
<i>to so flagrantly disrespect us.</i>

07:52.375 --> 07:55.000
<i>-What are you talking about?</i>
<i>-[woman 2] You abandoned us last night.</i>

07:55.083 --> 07:58.875
<i>We heard you went off with a random guy!</i>
<i>How do you think that'd make us feel?</i>

07:58.958 --> 08:01.250
<i>-All right. I'm sorry.</i>
<i>-[Nick] And on my birthday.</i>

08:01.333 --> 08:03.666
<i>I'm… I'm really sorry. Nick.</i>

08:05.000 --> 08:05.958
<i>I'm serious.</i>

08:09.500 --> 08:11.833
<i>Are you stressed? You seem stressed.</i>

08:11.916 --> 08:13.791
<i>Mary Ellen died,</i>
<i>and Janet wants a feature.</i>

08:13.875 --> 08:15.583
<i>There are not enough hours in the day.</i>

08:15.666 --> 08:17.291
<i>-When?</i>
<i>-Sunday's edition.</i>

08:17.375 --> 08:18.375
<i>No, when did she die?</i>

08:18.458 --> 08:20.250
<i>-A couple of days ago.</i>
<i>-That's so sad.</i>

08:20.333 --> 08:21.666
<i>-How?</i>
<i>-Yeah, old age.</i>

08:21.750 --> 08:24.500
<i>-Yeah?</i>
<i>-You know, I really wanna die that way.</i>

08:24.583 --> 08:26.625
<i>Why don't I take this one?</i>

08:26.708 --> 08:30.250
<i>I've got two hours left on this polish,</i>
<i>and then my schedule is wide open.</i>

08:31.333 --> 08:32.166
<i>Okay?</i>

08:34.125 --> 08:35.458
<i>Okay. Okay.</i>

08:35.958 --> 08:38.416
<i>Consider your load</i>
<i>officially lightened, my friend.</i>

08:38.500 --> 08:40.458
<i>-Morning, everyone.</i>
<i>-[group] Morning.</i>

08:40.541 --> 08:41.375
<i>How are we all?</i>

08:41.458 --> 08:42.708
<i>-[group] Good.</i>
<i>-Great.</i>

08:45.250 --> 08:48.333
<i>[footsteps approaching]</i>

08:48.416 --> 08:49.583
<i>-[Ellie] Hi.</i>
<i>-Hi.</i>

08:49.666 --> 08:50.791
<i>How you doing?</i>

08:50.875 --> 08:51.958
<i>Good. Thanks.</i>

08:52.625 --> 08:56.208
<i>Uh, I'm writing a feature on the paper's</i>
<i>longest-serving women's editor.</i>

08:57.208 --> 08:59.750
<i>-She just died.</i>
<i>-Yeah? Oh no.</i>

09:00.291 --> 09:01.125
<i>Yeah, no.</i>

09:01.208 --> 09:02.916
<i>It's my understanding she donated</i>

09:03.000 --> 09:04.666
<i>her collection of writings</i>
<i>to the Archives.</i>

09:04.750 --> 09:07.041
<i>What time was…</i>
<i>What's your appointment, sorry?</i>

09:07.125 --> 09:09.750
<i>Oh, no, sorry. I… um… I work here.</i>

09:09.833 --> 09:13.625
<i>Yeah, no, the thing is you…</i>
<i>you still need to make an appointment.</i>

09:13.708 --> 09:14.916
<i>-We can't--</i>
<i>-Even for staff?</i>

09:15.000 --> 09:16.458
<i>We don't just let people into the archive.</i>

09:16.541 --> 09:18.125
<i>Even though I work here.</i>

09:18.208 --> 09:19.958
<i>Yeah, no, sorry. Um…</i>

09:20.041 --> 09:24.375
<i>So if you… if you go online, um,</i>
<i>you can find our online catalog</i>

09:24.458 --> 09:26.875
<i>and then decide, uh,</i>
<i>whatever it is you wanna view.</i>

09:26.958 --> 09:28.625
<i>But I've done it a million times before--</i>

09:28.708 --> 09:32.916
<i>Yeah, um, and then either myself</i>
<i>or someone from the Archive team</i>

09:33.000 --> 09:34.208
<i>readies your documents.</i>

09:34.291 --> 09:37.000
<i>In which case, I would love</i>
<i>to make an appointment, please.</i>

09:38.500 --> 09:40.750
<i>Appointments have to be made</i>
<i>online through our…</i>

09:40.833 --> 09:41.916
<i>Seriously?</i>

09:42.000 --> 09:43.041
<i>…online portal.</i>

09:43.125 --> 09:44.291
<i>Online portal.</i>

09:44.375 --> 09:45.250
<i>You know what?</i>

09:46.125 --> 09:48.875
<i>Thanks so much</i>
<i>for all your help today, and</i>

09:48.958 --> 09:51.333
<i>I will see you again sometime soon.</i>

09:51.958 --> 09:54.458
<i>[footsteps walking away]</i>

09:54.541 --> 09:56.958
<i>-[playful instrumental music playing]</i>
<i>-[bell dings]</i>

10:03.791 --> 10:04.708
<i>[crumpling]</i>

10:18.666 --> 10:20.666
<i>[soft instrumental music playing]</i>

10:24.750 --> 10:26.083
<i>[car engine starts]</i>

10:58.791 --> 11:00.708
<i>[woman] I wish I could lose my memory.</i>

11:01.208 --> 11:05.291
<i>I'd run off into the sunset and forget</i>
<i>I ever married Francis in the first place.</i>

11:05.791 --> 11:06.625
<i>[laughs]</i>

11:07.375 --> 11:09.875
<i>Do you know how it happened?</i>
<i>Where I was going?</i>

11:09.958 --> 11:12.625
<i>Larry says you were out running errands.</i>

11:14.416 --> 11:16.416
<i>Beyond that, I'm sorry. I don't.</i>

11:17.416 --> 11:20.333
<i>-So you really don't remember anything?</i>
<i>-I remember in gaps.</i>

11:20.416 --> 11:24.041
<i>I don't know</i>
<i>how I'm meant to behave. I don't know….</i>

11:25.083 --> 11:27.541
<i>[sighs] I don't know</i>
<i>how I felt about my life.</i>

11:29.125 --> 11:30.291
<i>I don't…</i>

11:31.500 --> 11:34.166
<i>All right, darling. I'll fill you in.</i>

11:36.000 --> 11:41.333
<i>You were lovely and funny</i>
<i>and full of</i> <i>joie de vivre</i>.

11:42.791 --> 11:46.458
<i>You have the perfect life,</i>
<i>the cleverest best friend.</i>

11:47.583 --> 11:50.208
<i>The rich, handsome husband who adores you.</i>

11:50.291 --> 11:52.125
<i>Do you know why we don't have children?</i>

11:52.375 --> 11:54.750
<i>He's away an awful lot, your husband.</i>

11:55.708 --> 11:59.041
<i>It's one of the reasons</i>
<i>I've always been horribly envious of you.</i>

11:59.916 --> 12:01.875
<i>Oh, you'll be fine, darling.</i>

12:03.250 --> 12:06.541
<i>In the meantime, try to have fun tonight.</i>

12:06.625 --> 12:07.458
<i>Yeah.</i>

12:07.541 --> 12:09.041
<i>[woman 1] I don't believe it!</i>

12:09.125 --> 12:10.291
<i>Harold Wilson?</i>

12:10.375 --> 12:11.541
<i>The Harold Wilson?</i>

12:12.250 --> 12:13.208
<i>The very same.</i>

12:13.291 --> 12:14.333
<i>[woman 1 laughs]</i>

12:14.416 --> 12:17.041
<i>Please tell me</i>
<i>he took you somewhere scrumptious.</i>

12:17.125 --> 12:19.000
<i>-[Larry] Lockets.</i>
<i>-[group] Oh!</i>

12:19.500 --> 12:22.750
<i>[Larry's voice fading] His favorite place</i>
<i>to holiday is the Scilly Isles…</i>

12:22.833 --> 12:24.208
<i>[soft piano music playing]</i>

12:27.833 --> 12:30.208
<i>…party now has a chance</i>
<i>of getting a larger majority.</i>

12:30.291 --> 12:35.166
<i>[woman 1] Gentlemen, this is all well</i>
<i>and good, but what we really want to know</i>

12:35.250 --> 12:37.125
<i>is what does</i>
<i>the prime minister like for dessert?</i>

12:37.208 --> 12:38.541
<i>[group laughs]</i>

12:38.958 --> 12:40.583
<i>Darling, I think that's enough.</i>

12:41.791 --> 12:43.833
<i>-But it's just my second--</i>
<i>-Doctor's orders.</i>

12:45.500 --> 12:46.416
<i>Just water.</i>

12:48.458 --> 12:50.916
<i>[woman 2] Speaking of which,</i>
<i>you really don't remember anything?</i>

12:51.000 --> 12:52.625
<i>-[softly and brusquely] Anne!</i>
<i>-What?</i>

12:52.708 --> 12:55.041
<i>[Larry] How about some coffee? Anyone?</i>

12:55.125 --> 12:56.375
<i>[woman 1] Yes, please.</i>

12:56.458 --> 13:00.500
<i>[indistinct conversations among the group]</i>

13:00.583 --> 13:02.208
<i>[women laugh]</i>

13:04.583 --> 13:05.666
<i>[elevator bell dings]</i>

13:05.750 --> 13:07.750
<i>[soft instrumental music playing]</i>

13:16.000 --> 13:17.250
<i>[elevator bell dings]</i>

13:17.333 --> 13:19.125
<i>[playful instrumental music playing]</i>

13:19.208 --> 13:20.041
<i>Hi.</i>

13:20.666 --> 13:21.708
<i>-Hi.</i>
<i>-How you doing?</i>

13:22.541 --> 13:23.541
<i>Uh-huh.</i>

13:23.625 --> 13:24.666
<i>-You?</i>
<i>-Phenomenal.</i>

13:26.041 --> 13:28.500
<i>Um, everything's ready for you</i>
<i>in the reading room.</i>

13:28.583 --> 13:29.416
<i>Hmm.</i>

13:30.041 --> 13:31.333
<i>Spectacular.</i>

13:31.416 --> 13:34.125
<i>And sorry, we don't allow food and drink.</i>

13:36.333 --> 13:37.208
<i>[bag crinkles]</i>

13:38.083 --> 13:38.916
<i>Oh.</i>

13:44.791 --> 13:47.750
<i>[wrapper crinkling]</i>

13:47.833 --> 13:49.833
<i>[playful instrumental music playing]</i>

14:10.041 --> 14:10.875
<i>Hmm.</i>

14:16.666 --> 14:17.916
<i>Right this way.</i>

14:19.125 --> 14:24.333
<i>So, this is everything</i>
<i>from about '65 up until around '86, '87.</i>

14:24.416 --> 14:27.000
<i>These are her actual notebooks?</i>

14:27.083 --> 14:30.041
<i>Yep, they should be. Yeah.</i>

14:30.625 --> 14:31.708
<i>Thanks.</i>

14:34.291 --> 14:39.875
<i>Um, I just wanted to say quickly, uh,</i>
<i>I really enjoyed your, uh, feature on</i>

14:39.958 --> 14:42.916
<i>starter marriages</i>
<i>and all the, like, online dating stuff.</i>

14:43.000 --> 14:44.875
<i>-Oh yeah?</i>
<i>-Yeah, yeah.</i>

14:44.958 --> 14:50.333
<i>The bit about, you know, the difference</i>
<i>between passionate and companionate love.</i>

14:50.416 --> 14:53.041
<i>Yeah, I never really thought of it</i>
<i>like that before.</i>

14:53.708 --> 14:54.541
<i>Thanks.</i>

14:55.500 --> 14:57.000
<i>It gives me a warm, gooey feeling</i>

14:57.083 --> 15:00.125
<i>knowing my unadulterated misery</i>
<i>has finally been put to good use.</i>

15:00.666 --> 15:01.583
<i>[chuckles]</i>

15:03.333 --> 15:09.375
<i>So, um, how does someone like you end up</i>
<i>making their living as an archivist?</i>

15:09.458 --> 15:12.208
<i>I studied art history actually.</i>

15:12.291 --> 15:15.208
<i>And went on to do</i>
<i>a postgrad in Records Management, but…</i>

15:15.291 --> 15:18.625
<i>[fading] …um, you know,</i>
<i>at that point, I sort of realized,</i>

15:18.708 --> 15:22.291
<i>um, I sort of enjoy</i>
<i>categorizing stuff, oddly enough.</i>

15:22.375 --> 15:24.500
<i>And, you know,</i>
<i>people think it's a bit odd…</i>

15:24.583 --> 15:26.333
<i>[man] </i>My dearest and only love,

15:27.458 --> 15:28.750
<i>I know you're frightened,</i>

15:28.833 --> 15:32.000
<i>but believe me when I say</i>
<i>I've known nothing like this before</i>

15:32.083 --> 15:34.291
<i>and can assure that I never will again.</i>

15:35.125 --> 15:38.541
<i>I know I will never be satisfied</i>
<i>with just a part of you.</i>

15:38.625 --> 15:42.208
<i>And for that reason,</i>
<i>I'm going to take the job in New York.</i>

15:42.291 --> 15:46.083
<i>I'll be on platform two,</i>
<i>Marylebone, Friday, 7:15 p.m.</i>

15:47.041 --> 15:52.000
<i>Come with me, darling. Spare him a life</i>
<i>half-lived, a marriage of convenience.</i>

15:52.083 --> 15:54.250
<i>More importantly, spare yourself.</i>

15:54.333 --> 15:57.166
<i>Seize this thing</i>
<i>that is true and real and infinite.</i>

15:57.250 --> 16:00.875
<i>Yes, it is scary,</i>
<i>but I believe living a lie is worse.</i>

16:00.958 --> 16:02.333
<i>We could be happy.</i>

16:02.416 --> 16:03.708
<i>[man and Ellie] </i>So happy.

16:03.791 --> 16:07.208
<i>Know that you hold my heart,</i>
<i>my hopes in your hands.</i>

16:07.958 --> 16:09.416
<i>[Ellie] </i>Your Boot.

16:10.583 --> 16:11.916
<i>[archivist] …historical materials.</i>

16:12.000 --> 16:15.166
<i>-I… I… I think it's actually--</i>
<i>-Look at this!</i>

16:15.250 --> 16:16.083
<i>Huh?</i>

16:17.500 --> 16:19.291
<i>Um, what is it?</i>

16:19.375 --> 16:20.291
<i>It's a letter.</i>

16:29.500 --> 16:30.541
<i>Hmm. Jeez.</i>

16:30.625 --> 16:33.791
<i>Yeah, sad thing is if you're gonna elope</i>
<i>now, you'll probably just send a text.</i>

16:33.875 --> 16:34.708
<i>WhatsApp.</i>

16:34.791 --> 16:37.833
<i>Yeah, it'd be like, "Hey, babes, meet me</i>
<i>at the station if you're interested."</i>

16:37.916 --> 16:40.125
<i>#ComeWithIfYouWannaChangeYourLifeForever,</i>

16:40.208 --> 16:42.041
<i>smiley face, aubergine,</i>
<i>road sign, sausage.</i>

16:42.125 --> 16:45.083
<i>The worst thing is when you can see</i>
<i>they've read the message you've sent,</i>

16:45.166 --> 16:46.875
<i>and the little blue tick appears, and…</i>

16:46.958 --> 16:49.375
<i>-That's the worst.</i>
<i>-"Hello, I sent a message five days ago."</i>

16:49.458 --> 16:50.333
<i>Five hours ago!</i>

16:52.250 --> 16:53.833
<i>-I mean.</i>
<i>-Did I say days?</i>

16:54.541 --> 16:55.666
<i>I think so, yeah.</i>

16:57.375 --> 16:59.291
<i>-Can I see the envelope, please?</i>
<i>-Yeah.</i>

17:01.916 --> 17:05.666
<i>-"J.S." Must be in here by mistake.</i>
<i>-What do you think you will do with it?</i>

17:05.750 --> 17:06.583
<i>Burn it.</i>

17:06.666 --> 17:09.541
<i>No, I'm kidding. Probably make sure</i>
<i>it gets properly cataloged.</i>

17:09.625 --> 17:11.500
<i>Don't, what about returning it?</i>

17:12.750 --> 17:13.583
<i>[archivist] Hmm.</i>

17:14.000 --> 17:16.000
<i>Or trying to track down whoever sent it.</i>

17:17.125 --> 17:19.125
<i>[dramatic instrumental music playing]</i>

18:06.166 --> 18:09.750
<i>[Jenny] </i>"Dearest J, I know what
the situation cost you, darling Jenny."

18:10.708 --> 18:12.500
<i>"But I also know</i>
<i>that you and I could no more</i>

18:12.583 --> 18:15.583
<i>not love each other than the Earth</i>
<i>could stop circling the Sun."</i>

18:16.000 --> 18:19.166
<i>"You were upset the last time we parted,</i>
<i>and I cursed myself for it."</i>

18:19.875 --> 18:22.000
<i>"My frustration overwhelms me."</i>

18:22.333 --> 18:24.958
<i>"There is never enough time,</i>
<i>never enough of you."</i>

18:25.916 --> 18:28.708
<i>"Let's meet tomorrow. B."</i>

18:29.375 --> 18:30.458
<i>-[door opens]</i>
<i>-[gasps]</i>

18:31.416 --> 18:32.416
<i>[door closes]</i>

18:48.833 --> 18:51.833
<i>[suspenseful instrumental music playing]</i>

19:48.875 --> 19:50.333
<i>[Jenny] </i>"My darling J,

19:50.416 --> 19:54.041
<i>I'm still lost somewhere between our time</i>
<i>dancing the night away at Alberto's</i>

19:54.125 --> 19:55.791
<i>and being together on the Riviera."</i>

19:55.875 --> 19:56.708
<i>[scoffs] B?</i>

19:56.791 --> 19:58.875
<i>"Felipe told me I was like a drunken fool</i>

19:58.958 --> 20:01.250
<i>as I remembered</i>
<i>those summer days together."</i>

20:01.333 --> 20:04.166
<i>"If all we are allowed</i>
<i>are hours and minutes,</i>

20:04.250 --> 20:07.916
<i>I will etch them on to my memory</i>
<i>so I can recall them in the same way</i>

20:08.041 --> 20:11.333
<i>that when I close my eyes,</i>
<i>I see your heavenly face."</i>

20:12.000 --> 20:15.583
<i>"You are never far</i>
<i>from my thoughts. Your Boot."</i>

20:15.666 --> 20:18.083
<i>["Summer Wine" by Nancy Sinatra</i>
<i>and Lee Hazlewood playing]</i>

20:18.166 --> 20:23.333
<i>♪ Strawberries, cherries</i>
<i>And an angel's kiss in spring ♪</i>

20:24.541 --> 20:30.375
<i>♪ My summer wine is really made</i>
<i>From all these things ♪</i>

20:31.375 --> 20:37.583
<i>♪ Take off your silver spurs</i>
<i>And help me pass the time ♪</i>

20:38.166 --> 20:44.083
<i>♪ And I will give to you</i>
<i>Summer wine ♪</i>

20:44.166 --> 20:48.958
<i>♪ Oh, summer wine ♪</i>

20:51.833 --> 20:56.875
<i>♪ My eyes grew heavy</i>
<i>And my lips they could not speak ♪</i>

20:58.500 --> 21:03.625
<i>♪ I tried to get up</i>
<i>But I couldn't find my feet ♪</i>

21:05.333 --> 21:10.750
<i>♪ She reassured me</i>
<i>With an unfamiliar line ♪</i>

21:12.125 --> 21:16.250
<i>♪ And then she gave to me</i>
<i>More summer wine… ♪</i>

21:16.333 --> 21:20.333
<i>-[brakes engage]</i>
<i>-[car engine turns off]</i>

21:23.833 --> 21:24.708
<i>[car door shuts]</i>

21:26.750 --> 21:29.875
<i>-[door shuts]</i>
<i>-[Jenny and woman speaking French]</i>

21:31.041 --> 21:32.125
<i>[Larry] Good evening.</i>

21:37.166 --> 21:39.791
<i>Darling, don't forget</i>
<i>we have breakfast in the morning.</i>

21:40.125 --> 21:42.666
<i>[Larry] I have a journalist</i>
<i>coming tomorrow, first thing.</i>

21:44.333 --> 21:45.791
<i>I'll change it to lunch then.</i>

21:47.541 --> 21:49.750
<i>Dinner, darling. We have dinner.</i>

21:49.833 --> 21:50.666
<i>Larry.</i>

21:51.166 --> 21:52.000
<i>Let's not fuss.</i>

21:58.416 --> 22:00.166
<i>[waves crashing]</i>

22:06.541 --> 22:08.541
<i>[dramatic instrumental music playing]</i>

23:33.500 --> 23:34.458
<i>[woman] Can I help?</i>

23:36.916 --> 23:38.500
<i>[Jenny] Yes. [chuckles]</i>

23:38.583 --> 23:39.875
<i>I certainly am hoping so.</i>

23:45.333 --> 23:47.375
<i>Am I at all familiar to you?</i>

23:48.541 --> 23:50.666
<i>Don't ring any bells, I'm afraid.</i>

23:51.833 --> 23:54.125
<i>And what if I were to say the name Felipe?</i>

23:54.208 --> 23:55.708
<i>Would that mean anything to you?</i>

23:55.791 --> 23:58.083
<i>-[woman] Are you with the police?</i>
<i>-[Jenny] No.</i>

23:59.375 --> 24:01.833
<i>So why are you asking me about Felipe?</i>

24:02.958 --> 24:03.833
<i>Um…</i>

24:03.916 --> 24:05.875
<i>I believe we may have a mutual friend.</i>

24:05.958 --> 24:09.291
<i>Perhaps you might be able to tell me</i>
<i>where I could find him?</i>

24:09.375 --> 24:11.166
<i>[woman] I don't think you understand.</i>

24:12.333 --> 24:15.583
<i>Felipe was, uh, in an accident.</i>

24:16.500 --> 24:17.500
<i>He never woke up.</i>

24:17.583 --> 24:19.583
<i>[somber instrumental music playing]</i>

24:41.875 --> 24:43.416
<i>-[knocks at door]</i>
<i>-[door opens]</i>

24:43.791 --> 24:47.125
<i>Hey, um, just so you know, we usually have</i>
<i>to close the reading rooms around 5:00.</i>

24:47.208 --> 24:49.583
<i>[gasps] What time is it now?</i>

24:49.666 --> 24:50.833
<i>Coming up to 20 past.</i>

24:51.458 --> 24:53.583
<i>Shit. Okay. Um…</i>

24:54.208 --> 24:55.375
<i>I'll be two secs.</i>

24:55.458 --> 24:57.458
<i>[footsteps approaching]</i>

25:01.541 --> 25:04.458
<i>So, uh, did you find everything all right?</i>

25:04.541 --> 25:07.041
<i>Yeah. Yeah, I guess so.</i>

25:08.000 --> 25:11.750
<i>I mean, if I want to request more stuff,</i>
<i>then I have to go on the, um…</i>

25:11.833 --> 25:14.333
<i>-Via the online. Yeah, same process.</i>
<i>-Via the online.</i>

25:14.416 --> 25:15.916
<i>-The…</i>
<i>-Online portal.</i>

25:16.000 --> 25:17.250
<i>-Process.</i>
<i>-Yeah.</i>

25:22.708 --> 25:24.375
<i>-[Ellie] Where you headed?</i>
<i>-Basement.</i>

25:24.458 --> 25:25.833
<i>[presses three buttons]</i>

25:27.791 --> 25:29.875
<i>Um, what if I wanted to see if there were</i>

25:29.958 --> 25:32.541
<i>any more of those letters?</i>
<i>Could be a story in it.</i>

25:32.625 --> 25:36.750
<i>If you wanted to,</i>
<i>you could just send me an email, actually.</i>

25:36.833 --> 25:39.333
<i>-If you wanted to speed things up a bit.</i>
<i>-Oh.</i>

25:40.875 --> 25:41.708
<i>Thanks.</i>

25:43.500 --> 25:45.291
<i>Turning into a real rebel.</i>

25:45.375 --> 25:46.250
<i>[bell dings]</i>

25:47.291 --> 25:48.125
<i>Have a good one.</i>

25:51.708 --> 25:52.583
<i>Have a good week.</i>

26:05.291 --> 26:09.833
<i>-[footsteps approaching]</i>
<i>-[woman speaking French]</i>

26:10.500 --> 26:11.875
<i>Anthony O'Hare.</i>

26:13.666 --> 26:15.083
<i>[Jenny] Oh, yes.</i>

26:15.166 --> 26:17.666
<i>You're here to write marvelous things</i>
<i>about my husband, I believe.</i>

26:17.750 --> 26:19.083
<i>Is that right?</i>

26:19.166 --> 26:23.083
<i>"Beacon of sound commercial practice,</i>
<i>turnover increasing year after year."</i>

26:23.166 --> 26:26.875
<i>-Are you asking me or telling me?</i>
<i>-I'm his wife. I can hardly be impartial.</i>

26:26.958 --> 26:29.625
<i>In my experience, there's no one</i>
<i>more brutally impartial than a wife.</i>

26:29.708 --> 26:31.041
<i>[chuckles] Indeed.</i>

26:34.333 --> 26:36.500
<i>I'm afraid Larry is running a little late.</i>

26:37.000 --> 26:38.750
<i>Perhaps not so marvelous after all.</i>

26:40.375 --> 26:41.208
<i>[chuckles]</i>

26:41.958 --> 26:44.458
<i>Um, may we offer you</i>
<i>a drink in the meantime?</i>

26:45.583 --> 26:46.750
<i>No, thank you.</i>

26:48.833 --> 26:49.875
<i>Mr. O'Hare.</i>

26:49.958 --> 26:50.875
<i>Mr. Stirling.</i>

26:50.958 --> 26:53.208
<i>-Please accept my apologies.</i>
<i>-Not a problem.</i>

26:53.291 --> 26:56.000
<i>-Shall we start?</i>
<i>-Ah, yeah. I'm ready whenever you are.</i>

26:59.583 --> 27:03.041
<i>[laughing] I don't know how</i>
<i>I didn't end up in the most awful trouble.</i>

27:03.125 --> 27:06.333
<i>What about you, Mr. O'Hare?</i>
<i>You're a financial journalist.</i>

27:06.416 --> 27:09.500
<i>-Foreign correspondent.</i>
<i>-[woman] Where have you been recently?</i>

27:09.583 --> 27:12.375
<i>Well, Léopoldville, mainly. Brazzaville.</i>

27:12.458 --> 27:14.375
<i>Godawful place if you ask me.</i>

27:14.458 --> 27:17.500
<i>[man] And where this evening's exemplary</i>
<i>host has a great deal of business.</i>

27:17.583 --> 27:19.041
<i>Well, I think that--</i>

27:19.125 --> 27:21.166
<i>I felt the Belgians</i>
<i>were doing a perfectly good job</i>

27:21.250 --> 27:22.583
<i>of running the place themselves.</i>

27:22.666 --> 27:26.333
<i>With respect, I was there</i>
<i>in '59, '60, and again in '62--</i>

27:26.416 --> 27:27.916
<i>So you of all people should understand</i>

27:28.000 --> 27:30.833
<i>that mutiny and rebellion</i>
<i>are an inferior and foolhardy response--</i>

27:30.916 --> 27:32.166
<i>To centuries of oppression?</i>

27:33.333 --> 27:35.291
<i>I would suggest that taking back control</i>

27:35.375 --> 27:38.333
<i>politically, geographically</i>
<i>is an entirely appropriate--</i>

27:38.416 --> 27:41.291
<i>Would one be correct in assuming</i>
<i>that you are a supporter of Mr. Mobutu's?</i>

27:41.375 --> 27:43.625
<i>Larry, Mobutu's a dictator.</i>
<i>I doubt very much--</i>

27:43.708 --> 27:46.250
<i>Yes, darling, I am aware.</i>
<i>Thank you. [chuckles]</i>

27:46.333 --> 27:50.375
<i>[woman] Enough, enough. This is all</i>
<i>far too depressing for the dinner table.</i>

27:50.458 --> 27:52.916
<i>[man 2] My wife considers</i>
<i>anything not in the pages of </i>Vogue

27:53.000 --> 27:54.916
<i>unworthy of her time and attention.</i>

27:55.000 --> 27:56.541
<i>[group laughs]</i>

27:59.375 --> 28:01.333
<i>[O'Hare] I'll get out and meet</i>
<i>as many people as possible,</i>

28:01.416 --> 28:03.708
<i>travel the world because people like that,</i>

28:04.708 --> 28:08.541
<i>they make me want to stick a revolver</i>
<i>in my mouth and pull the trigger.</i>

28:08.625 --> 28:10.000
<i>And the women, Jesus!</i>

28:11.000 --> 28:12.041
<i>Spoiled little tai-tais</i>

28:12.125 --> 28:14.791
<i>with barely an original thought</i>
<i>to string together between them--</i>

28:14.875 --> 28:16.750
<i>I'm sorry we were such a disappointment.</i>

28:18.333 --> 28:20.541
<i>Christ, I'm, uh… I'm drunk.</i>

28:20.625 --> 28:21.541
<i>Evidently.</i>

28:22.208 --> 28:25.208
<i>Perhaps, the next time you find yourself</i>
<i>in the company of such bores,</i>

28:25.291 --> 28:26.500
<i>you'd do well to leave early.</i>

28:26.583 --> 28:29.041
<i>I just ask that whatever your views</i>
<i>of me and my spoiled life,</i>

28:29.125 --> 28:30.708
<i>you won't attack Larry in print.</i>

28:31.333 --> 28:32.333
<i>Please excuse me.</i>

28:40.041 --> 28:44.041
<i>[woman] Goodness, I have</i>
<i>the most splitting headache. Last night.</i>

28:44.125 --> 28:45.625
<i>[Ellie] Did you really drink that much?</i>

28:45.708 --> 28:47.791
<i>I have a fine feeling I did.</i>

28:52.208 --> 28:54.083
<i>-Mr. O'Hare.</i>
<i>-Mrs. Stirling.</i>

28:56.916 --> 28:57.916
<i>What are you doing?</i>

28:58.000 --> 28:58.833
<i>Uh.</i>

28:59.958 --> 29:01.666
<i>I wanted to give you…</i>

29:04.041 --> 29:05.041
<i>this.</i>

29:06.166 --> 29:07.458
<i>What is it?</i>

29:07.541 --> 29:08.666
<i>It's an apology.</i>

29:09.250 --> 29:10.083
<i>Well, please.</i>

29:11.250 --> 29:12.458
<i>-Read it.</i>
<i>-Jennifer. [chuckles]</i>

29:12.541 --> 29:16.458
<i>Mr. O'Hare has written it. I'm sure he's</i>
<i>perfectly capable of reading it aloud.</i>

29:19.833 --> 29:23.000
<i>[paper unfolds]</i>

29:23.083 --> 29:24.291
<i>"Mrs. Stirling…</i>

29:25.375 --> 29:27.500
<i>I am an ungracious pig."</i>

29:28.333 --> 29:30.333
<i>"I'd like to be able to blame exhaustion</i>

29:30.416 --> 29:32.833
<i>or some uncharacteristic reaction</i>
<i>to shellfish,</i>

29:32.916 --> 29:35.541
<i>but I am afraid</i>
<i>it was the combination of the alcohol,</i>

29:35.625 --> 29:39.250
<i>which I shouldn't take, and the</i>
<i>choleric temper of the socially inept."</i>

29:40.083 --> 29:42.875
<i>"There is little you could say</i>
<i>about me that I have not already deduced</i>

29:42.958 --> 29:45.500
<i>about myself in my more sober hours."</i>

29:45.583 --> 29:48.458
<i>"Please allow me to apologize."</i>

29:48.541 --> 29:53.291
<i>"Yours shamefacedly, Anthony O'Hare."</i>

29:55.875 --> 29:59.125
<i>If at all possible, I'd love</i>
<i>to take you and your husband to lunch.</i>

29:59.208 --> 30:01.208
<i>Hmm. How very kind of you.</i>

30:03.291 --> 30:04.291
<i>I'll think on it.</i>

30:04.791 --> 30:07.291
<i>In the meantime,</i>
<i>I must return you to your hotel.</i>

30:08.083 --> 30:10.291
<i>I won't be responsible</i>
<i>for you contracting sunstroke.</i>

30:10.375 --> 30:12.375
<i>Not to mention alcohol poisoning.</i>

30:13.166 --> 30:14.166
<i>[woman laughs]</i>

30:14.250 --> 30:15.291
<i>Yes.</i>

30:15.375 --> 30:16.208
<i>Please.</i>

30:17.083 --> 30:18.083
<i>Thank you.</i>

30:18.166 --> 30:20.125
<i>[upbeat guitar music playing]</i>

30:37.916 --> 30:39.041
<i>Larry.</i>

30:40.375 --> 30:42.750
<i>-Mr. O'Hare.</i>
<i>-Mr. Stirling. How are you?</i>

30:42.833 --> 30:44.541
<i>-Very well. Thank you.</i>
<i>-Mrs. Stirling.</i>

30:44.625 --> 30:45.583
<i>Hi.</i>

30:45.666 --> 30:46.500
<i>[O'Hare] How are you?</i>

30:47.000 --> 30:48.041
<i>I'm fine. Thank you.</i>

30:56.125 --> 30:57.166
<i>[chuckles]</i>

30:58.208 --> 31:00.750
<i>Tell me, Mr. O'Hare.</i>
<i>Is there a Mrs. O'Hare?</i>

31:02.250 --> 31:05.208
<i>Yes, there was.</i>
<i>Uh, Mrs. O'Hare and I divorced.</i>

31:06.166 --> 31:07.916
<i>Well, you have my condolences.</i>

31:08.000 --> 31:09.208
<i>It's a ghastly business.</i>

31:10.958 --> 31:12.875
<i>-[Larry] Children?</i>
<i>-Larry, for goodness sake.</i>

31:12.958 --> 31:16.916
<i>No, no, no, it's quite all right.</i>
<i>Yes, I have one son, Peter.</i>

31:17.000 --> 31:20.000
<i>I was at Gordonstoun</i>
<i>with a terrific chap by the name of Peter.</i>

31:20.083 --> 31:22.041
<i>-[man speaking French]</i>
<i>-English.</i>

31:23.583 --> 31:24.791
<i>Where are you off to next?</i>

31:24.875 --> 31:27.583
<i>After I finish the piece,</i>
<i>back home to London.</i>

31:27.666 --> 31:28.916
<i>[chair scoots out]</i>

31:29.000 --> 31:30.416
<i>-Excuse me.</i>
<i>-[O'Hare] Of course.</i>

31:36.458 --> 31:37.333
<i>I apologize.</i>

31:39.541 --> 31:40.375
<i>It's okay.</i>

31:42.833 --> 31:44.041
<i>Aren't you drinking?</i>

31:44.750 --> 31:46.958
<i>Um, no, I'm not meant to.</i>

31:47.041 --> 31:47.958
<i>A headache?</i>

31:48.916 --> 31:49.916
<i>Doctor's orders.</i>

31:50.000 --> 31:52.250
<i>So you really found</i>
<i>last night that unbearable?</i>

31:52.333 --> 31:55.750
<i>I admit it. I find armed conflict</i>
<i>a less daunting prospect.</i>

31:55.833 --> 31:59.500
<i>[laughs] You're William Boot from </i>Scoop<i>.</i>

32:00.708 --> 32:03.166
<i>-Evelyn Waugh?</i>
<i>-I know who William Boot is.</i>

32:04.125 --> 32:10.708
<i>[man speaking French]</i>

32:10.791 --> 32:13.541
<i>[speaking French]</i>

32:15.083 --> 32:16.125
<i>Is everything all right?</i>

32:16.875 --> 32:18.833
<i>Duty calls. [chuckles]</i>

32:24.000 --> 32:28.708
<i>[inhales deeply] Tell me, Mr. O'Hare.</i>
<i>How are your sea legs?</i>

32:28.791 --> 32:30.791
<i>[whimsical instrumental music playing]</i>

32:42.000 --> 32:42.958
<i>Thank you.</i>

32:43.541 --> 32:44.458
<i>What do you think?</i>

32:46.458 --> 32:47.291
<i>Big.</i>

32:47.750 --> 32:49.500
<i>[laughs] Of the view.</i>

32:51.666 --> 32:52.500
<i>[O'Hare] Hmm.</i>

32:55.458 --> 32:56.541
<i>[Jenny] See that over there?</i>

32:57.875 --> 32:59.041
<i>It's Corsica.</i>

33:03.083 --> 33:03.958
<i>You travel a lot?</i>

33:04.041 --> 33:05.208
<i>I don't, actually.</i>

33:08.125 --> 33:11.958
<i>We come here every summer, but I haven't</i>
<i>been back overseas since we married,</i>

33:12.041 --> 33:13.375
<i>not even to see family.</i>

33:13.458 --> 33:15.125
<i>Larry does all the traveling now.</i>

33:17.791 --> 33:18.833
<i>How'd you two meet?</i>

33:18.916 --> 33:20.583
<i>[chuckles]</i>

33:20.666 --> 33:23.625
<i>We were seated next to one another</i>
<i>at a company dinner in New York.</i>

33:23.708 --> 33:26.750
<i>Our fathers used to work together.</i>
<i>He asked me out, and that was that.</i>

33:26.833 --> 33:27.833
<i>That simple?</i>

33:28.708 --> 33:31.583
<i>It was. A few months later,</i>
<i>he asked me to marry him, and I said yes.</i>

33:31.666 --> 33:33.708
<i>My parents were delighted.</i>

33:33.791 --> 33:34.750
<i>How so?</i>

33:34.833 --> 33:37.333
<i>Good family. Good job.</i>

33:37.416 --> 33:39.583
<i>Those things are important</i>
<i>to you, are they?</i>

33:41.041 --> 33:42.250
<i>Aren't they to everyone?</i>

33:42.333 --> 33:43.166
<i>I guess so.</i>

33:43.750 --> 33:45.625
<i>I want you to tell me about your son.</i>

33:46.500 --> 33:47.583
<i>-My son?</i>
<i>-Hmm.</i>

33:47.666 --> 33:52.208
<i>Lives with my ex-wife who does her best</i>
<i>to make sure I don't corrupt him.</i>

33:52.291 --> 33:55.000
<i>And why would she think</i>
<i>you would corrupt him? [chuckles]</i>

33:55.875 --> 33:57.125
<i>Because I was unfaithful.</i>

34:03.208 --> 34:04.250
<i>You must miss him.</i>

34:05.666 --> 34:06.500
<i>I do.</i>

34:07.875 --> 34:11.583
<i>Sometimes I wonder whether if I'd've done</i>
<i>what I did if I'd've known quite how much.</i>

34:11.666 --> 34:12.875
<i>Is that why you drink?</i>

34:13.791 --> 34:15.958
<i>Don't try to fix me, Mrs. Stirling.</i>

34:16.041 --> 34:17.541
<i>Who said I was trying--</i>

34:17.625 --> 34:20.708
<i>Oh, you have that charitable air</i>
<i>about you. It makes me feel nervous.</i>

34:20.791 --> 34:23.666
<i>[scoffs] Well, I'm guessing</i>
<i>I wouldn't be the first.</i>

34:25.333 --> 34:26.708
<i>You'd make a very good journalist.</i>

34:27.458 --> 34:29.333
<i>Did you love her? Your wife?</i>

34:29.416 --> 34:33.750
<i>I thought I did before, but we were young,</i>
<i>and I'm not sure I knew what love was.</i>

34:33.833 --> 34:37.208
<i>-Have you ever loved anyone?</i>
<i>-My son. Have you ever loved anyone?</i>

34:38.291 --> 34:39.250
<i>I'm married.</i>

34:40.041 --> 34:40.875
<i>You are.</i>

34:46.250 --> 34:47.083
<i>[clears throat]</i>

34:48.500 --> 34:51.416
<i>For the record,</i>
<i>Larry and I are perfectly content.</i>

34:53.458 --> 34:54.500
<i>I'm glad to hear it.</i>

35:01.791 --> 35:03.416
<i>[typing]</i>

35:15.500 --> 35:16.708
<i>[phone ringing]</i>

35:24.791 --> 35:25.833
<i>Features.</i>

35:25.916 --> 35:29.791
<i>[man] </i>Yeah, hi, I was wondering
if I could speak to Ellie Haworth, please?

35:29.875 --> 35:30.750
<i>Speaking.</i>

35:31.375 --> 35:34.291
<i>[man] </i>Oh, hi. Yeah, it's…
it's Rory from Archive.

35:34.375 --> 35:38.125
<i>I think I might have maybe found something</i>
<i>you might want to come and take a look at.</i>

35:41.833 --> 35:43.000
<i>[Rory] Hi, hi. Is, oh--</i>

35:43.083 --> 35:45.041
<i>-Uh, is that gum?</i>
<i>-Uh-huh.</i>

35:45.125 --> 35:47.875
<i>Yeah, we don't… we don't love gum</i>
<i>in the reading rooms.</i>

35:51.250 --> 35:53.083
<i>-Swallowed it.</i>
<i>-Great.</i>

35:53.166 --> 35:54.791
<i>Okay. Um…</i>

35:54.875 --> 35:56.333
<i>I found another letter.</i>

36:04.500 --> 36:06.541
<i>[Ellie] </i>"It's 4:00 a.m.,
and I can't sleep."

36:06.625 --> 36:08.208
<i>"It's lik</i>e The Road to Madness,

36:08.291 --> 36:10.583
<i>but I lie here imagining him next to you,</i>

36:10.666 --> 36:13.250
<i>his license to touch you, to hold you,</i>

36:13.333 --> 36:16.208
<i>and I would do anything</i>
<i>to make that freedom mine."</i>

36:16.291 --> 36:19.500
<i>"For as long as I can't have you,</i>
<i>I'll conjure you here instead."</i>

36:20.208 --> 36:21.875
<i>"Your scent, your hair,</i>

36:21.958 --> 36:25.416
<i>that slow sideways smile</i>
<i>when something I say amuses you."</i>

36:26.083 --> 36:30.333
<i>"Darling J, I've never wished harder</i>
<i>for the dawn. Your Boot."</i>

36:30.416 --> 36:32.750
<i>Mmm. It's definitely…</i>

36:33.791 --> 36:35.166
<i>Definitely the same.</i>

36:35.250 --> 36:38.666
<i>Yeah, it's the same kind</i>
<i>of envelope, same handwriting.</i>

36:38.750 --> 36:40.625
<i>Now I'm going</i>
<i>to have to know how it ends,</i>

36:40.708 --> 36:44.291
<i>which means not only is the rest of my day</i>
<i>fucked, but, guess what, so is yours.</i>

36:44.375 --> 36:45.458
<i>How fucked are we talking?</i>

36:45.541 --> 36:48.250
<i>Well, I have to know</i>
<i>if there are more of these.</i>

36:48.958 --> 36:50.083
<i>Uh, yes, um…</i>

36:50.166 --> 36:54.000
<i>The only problem is, at this stage, um,</i>
<i>if we're gonna find out if there are more,</i>

36:54.083 --> 36:56.416
<i>it's probably gonna require</i>
<i>going down to the actual archive.</i>

36:56.500 --> 36:57.958
<i>Great! Oh my God! Let's do it!</i>

36:58.041 --> 37:00.041
<i>Yeah, but to do that,</i>
<i>we need a special permission.</i>

37:00.125 --> 37:00.958
<i>Um…</i>

37:01.708 --> 37:02.625
<i>How do we do that?</i>

37:03.833 --> 37:08.500
<i>Well, there's a form, and then after that</i>
<i>is probably, well, another form, actually.</i>

37:08.583 --> 37:09.833
<i>Sounds… sounds easy enough.</i>

37:09.916 --> 37:11.666
<i>Let me… let me see what I can do.</i>

37:12.666 --> 37:13.625
<i>Thank you.</i>

37:18.166 --> 37:19.750
<i>-Cool.</i>
<i>-Cool.</i>

37:20.791 --> 37:25.375
<i>["This Little Bird"</i>
<i>by Marianne Faithful playing]</i>

37:25.458 --> 37:27.458
<i>[indistinct talking]</i>

37:29.666 --> 37:35.750
<i>♪ There's a little bird</i>
<i>That somebody sends ♪</i>

37:37.166 --> 37:43.875
<i>♪ Down to the earth to live on the wind ♪</i>

37:45.333 --> 37:52.333
<i>♪ Born on the wind</i>
<i>And he sleeps on the wind ♪</i>

37:53.708 --> 38:00.125
<i>♪ This little bird that somebody sends ♪</i>

38:01.500 --> 38:07.791
<i>♪ He's light and fragile</i>
<i>And feathered sky blue ♪</i>

38:09.458 --> 38:16.125
<i>♪ So thin and graceful</i>
<i>The sun shines through… ♪</i>

38:16.208 --> 38:19.041
<i>[Jenny] </i>Dear Mr. O'Hare,
or shall I call you Boot?

38:19.125 --> 38:21.250
<i>Larry called away overseas last minute.</i>

38:21.750 --> 38:24.625
<i>It would appear we are both</i>
<i>marooned here until he returns.</i>

38:24.708 --> 38:28.250
<i>And you without proper beach attire,</i>
<i>how embarrassing.</i>

38:28.333 --> 38:31.333
<i>Care to pass the time</i>
<i>together this afternoon?</i>

38:31.416 --> 38:34.875
<i>I know a darling little shop where</i>
<i>you could find your next seaside tome.</i>

38:34.958 --> 38:37.583
<i>Yours, J.</i>

38:41.708 --> 38:44.041
<i>♪ Borne on the wind ♪</i>

38:44.125 --> 38:46.625
<i>[O'Hare] </i>Dear Mrs. Stirling,
or may I call you J?

38:46.708 --> 38:49.250
<i>Thank you for the offer</i>
<i>and frankly, for the rescue.</i>

38:49.333 --> 38:52.583
<i>I'm indebted to you for persuading me</i>
<i>out of my room yesterday.</i>

38:52.666 --> 38:54.791
<i>I would love to return the favor.</i>

38:54.875 --> 38:58.125
<i>I know nowhere, of course,</i>
<i>but if you can suggest a place,</i>

38:58.208 --> 39:01.125
<i>I can keep you laughing</i>
<i>with my terrible schoolboy French.</i>

39:01.208 --> 39:03.958
<i>[Jenny] Dear Boot, I'm delighted</i>
<i>I managed to propel you,</i>

39:04.041 --> 39:05.666
<i>blinking, into the sunlight.</i>

39:06.208 --> 39:08.875
<i>I would be happy</i>
<i> to take you up on your invitation.</i>

39:08.958 --> 39:12.083
<i>Perhaps we can spend a few hours</i>
<i>in town commiserating over our mutual</i>

39:12.166 --> 39:16.250
<i>inadequacies with the local language.</i>
<i>Are you free on Thursday?</i>

39:16.333 --> 39:20.958
<i>[O'Hare] </i>I'm free Thursday, but
I'm also free tomorrow and the day after

39:21.041 --> 39:22.583
<i>and the day after that as well.</i>

39:22.666 --> 39:24.791
<i>By the time Mr. Stirling returns,</i>

39:24.875 --> 39:27.250
<i>we could very well cover</i>
<i>the entire coastline.</i>

39:28.083 --> 39:30.791
<i>Let me know what time suits you. Boot.</i>

39:32.375 --> 39:38.041
<i>-♪ Out of reach of human eye ♪</i>
<i>-</i>[Jenny laughing]

39:40.208 --> 39:47.208
<i>♪ And the only time</i>
<i>That he touches the ground ♪</i>

39:48.291 --> 39:51.666
<i>♪ Is when that little bird ♪</i>

39:52.458 --> 39:55.625
<i>♪ Is when that little bird ♪</i>

39:56.416 --> 40:02.000
<i>♪ Is when that little bird dies ♪</i>

40:06.875 --> 40:07.958
<i>[thundering]</i>

40:08.041 --> 40:09.000
<i>[Jenny shrieks]</i>

40:09.083 --> 40:11.291
<i>[chuckles]</i>

40:11.375 --> 40:13.083
<i>[groans and gasps]</i>

40:13.166 --> 40:15.625
<i>[panting]</i>

40:16.291 --> 40:18.083
<i>[both chuckle]</i>

40:19.541 --> 40:21.875
<i>-[Jenny panting] Thank you.</i>
<i>-You're welcome.</i>

40:23.625 --> 40:27.291
<i>-[keys jingle]</i>
<i>-[engine cranking]</i>

40:30.583 --> 40:32.583
<i>[engine continues cranking]</i>

40:36.333 --> 40:37.458
<i>[Jenny] Any ideas?</i>

40:37.541 --> 40:40.875
<i>[engine cranking]</i>

40:41.750 --> 40:43.000
<i>How about a picnic?</i>

40:43.916 --> 40:46.875
<i>It's a children's game that I used to play</i>
<i>with my son. Do you know it?</i>

40:48.375 --> 40:49.708
<i>You need to close your eyes.</i>

40:50.416 --> 40:52.333
<i>-Come on, close them.</i>
<i>-[chuckles]</i>

40:56.000 --> 40:57.250
<i>Pick a favorite spot.</i>

40:58.708 --> 40:59.666
<i>Real or imagined?</i>

40:59.750 --> 41:00.583
<i>Either.</i>

41:01.250 --> 41:04.708
<i>Imagine that we have everything we need,</i>
<i>the perfect blanket, plenty of cheese.</i>

41:04.791 --> 41:07.875
<i>-Bread?</i>
<i>-Bread, and there's a river nearby.</i>

41:07.958 --> 41:08.791
<i>Oh, a river.</i>

41:08.875 --> 41:10.416
<i>And my son, he loves to, uh, fish.</i>

41:10.500 --> 41:14.708
<i>So I hope you don't mind, um,</i>
<i>we try our hand at a little fishing.</i>

41:14.791 --> 41:17.500
<i>I'm afraid</i>
<i>I know next to nothing about fishing.</i>

41:17.583 --> 41:19.208
<i>Which is why I'm going to teach you.</i>

41:19.958 --> 41:22.375
<i>[chuckles] How am I doing, Mr. Boot?</i>

41:23.125 --> 41:25.958
<i>You're a natural, as it goes.</i>

41:26.041 --> 41:27.791
<i>Of course I am. [chuckles]</i>

41:28.666 --> 41:30.875
<i>And you catch a trout.</i>

41:30.958 --> 41:31.791
<i>Shark.</i>

41:31.875 --> 41:33.208
<i>Shark. Excellent work.</i>

41:35.750 --> 41:36.916
<i>And afterwards…</i>

41:39.833 --> 41:43.041
<i>out of the leftover teeth,</i>
<i>I fashion you a necklace.</i>

41:45.166 --> 41:46.125
<i>A souvenir.</i>

41:48.000 --> 41:48.833
<i>A talisman.</i>

41:49.333 --> 41:51.708
<i>[soft instrumental music playing]</i>

42:01.333 --> 42:03.625
<i>-Let's try again. Shall we?</i>
<i>-[engine cranking]</i>

42:05.333 --> 42:06.583
<i>[engine turns over]</i>

42:15.625 --> 42:17.958
<i>Thank you</i>
<i>for an immensely agreeable afternoon.</i>

42:26.208 --> 42:27.166
<i>Until next time.</i>

42:46.625 --> 42:50.125
<i>[cell phone buzzing]</i>

42:50.208 --> 42:51.916
<i>["Lonesome" by Velvet Dos playing]</i>

42:52.000 --> 42:54.958
<i>♪ Your love is like a drug ♪</i>

42:55.041 --> 43:01.416
<i>♪ That’s why I can’t get enough ♪</i>

43:07.125 --> 43:11.291
<i>♪ I’m lonesome for your touch ♪</i>

43:11.375 --> 43:18.375
<i>♪ That’s why I can’t get enough ♪</i>

43:20.500 --> 43:21.750
<i>[text message whooshing]</i>

43:26.166 --> 43:28.250
<i>[Ellie] </i>Mary Ellen piece
proofed and attached.

43:28.333 --> 43:30.625
<i>Oh, and another thing,</i>
<i>while I was researching,</i>

43:30.708 --> 43:34.208
<i>I came across some mysterious</i>
<i>old love letters among her things.</i>

43:34.291 --> 43:37.625
<i>Not sure how or why they ended up there,</i>
<i>but digging into it for my next feature,</i>

43:37.708 --> 43:40.583
<i>1965, illicit love affair.</i>

43:40.666 --> 43:43.708
<i>They're so rich in feeling.</i>
<i>I've never read anything quite like it.</i>

43:43.791 --> 43:45.416
<i>Have it to you by Friday.</i>

43:49.583 --> 43:55.583
<i>[Jenny and man speaking French]</i>

43:57.208 --> 44:01.583
<i>[rotary phone dialing]</i>

44:02.916 --> 44:05.500
<i>[man speaking French]</i>

44:06.583 --> 44:07.458
<i>[sighs deeply]</i>

44:08.375 --> 44:11.250
<i>-[man speaking French]</i>
<i>-[phone hangs up]</i>

44:13.708 --> 44:16.458
<i>[man in French] Mr. O'Hare</i>
<i>isn't quite ready yet.</i>

44:16.541 --> 44:19.791
<i>He suggests either you are very welcome</i>
<i>to wait down here or head upstairs.</i>

44:20.291 --> 44:21.416
<i>Room 302.</i>

44:21.500 --> 44:22.916
<i>[Jenny and man speak French]</i>

44:40.416 --> 44:43.833
<i>["Do Right Woman, Do Right Man"</i>
<i>by Aretha Franklin playing faintly]</i>

44:53.708 --> 44:55.375
<i>-[Jenny chuckles]</i>
<i>-What a lovely surprise.</i>

44:55.458 --> 44:58.791
<i>Sorry. I'm a little early.</i>
<i>Would you rather I waited downstairs?</i>

44:58.875 --> 45:01.375
<i>No. Don't be silly. Come in.</i>

45:01.458 --> 45:03.458
<i>[music plays at normal level]</i>

45:03.583 --> 45:04.541
<i>I won't be long.</i>

45:06.375 --> 45:08.083
<i>I was just about to have a shave.</i>

45:08.833 --> 45:10.458
<i>-Oh.</i>
<i>-Do I have time?</i>

45:10.541 --> 45:11.791
<i>Of course, go ahead.</i>

45:11.875 --> 45:13.791
<i>♪ Take me for granted ♪</i>

45:15.791 --> 45:20.125
<i>♪ Leaving love unsure ♪</i>

45:22.500 --> 45:24.750
<i>♪ Makes willpower weak ♪</i>

45:24.833 --> 45:26.000
<i>Is everything all right?</i>

45:26.458 --> 45:28.041
<i>Yes, yes. Fine.</i>

45:28.125 --> 45:30.125
<i>♪ And temptation strong ♪</i>

45:35.958 --> 45:37.791
<i>♪ A woman's only human ♪</i>

45:41.250 --> 45:43.250
<i>♪ You should understand ♪</i>

45:45.916 --> 45:47.708
<i>♪ She's not just a plaything</i>… <i>♪</i>

45:47.791 --> 45:49.041
<i>I've received a wire.</i>

45:50.708 --> 45:53.250
<i>Larry's back this evening.</i>

45:54.541 --> 45:56.458
<i>He is to return to London immediately.</i>

45:59.375 --> 46:00.208
<i>[O'Hare] I see.</i>

46:05.166 --> 46:06.333
<i>And what do you want?</i>

46:06.416 --> 46:12.708
<i>♪ You've got to be</i>
<i>A do-right-all-night man ♪</i>

46:16.500 --> 46:21.583
<i>♪ Yeah, yeah</i>
<i>They say that it's a man's world ♪</i>

46:23.541 --> 46:26.583
<i>♪ But you can't prove that by me ♪</i>

46:28.416 --> 46:31.416
<i>♪ And as long as we're together</i>,<i> baby ♪</i>

46:32.625 --> 46:36.083
<i>♪ Show some respect for me ♪</i>

46:36.750 --> 46:37.875
<i>[O'Hare whispers] I'm sorry.</i>

46:37.958 --> 46:40.916
<i>♪ If you want a do-right-all-day woman</i>… <i>♪</i>

46:41.000 --> 46:42.125
<i>[Jenny softly] Oh God.</i>

46:44.416 --> 46:45.250
<i>Jennifer.</i>

46:46.333 --> 46:47.166
<i>Jennifer.</i>

46:49.458 --> 46:50.291
<i>[sighs]</i>

46:50.375 --> 46:52.333
<i>[dramatic instrumental music playing]</i>

46:55.583 --> 46:57.583
<i>[speaking indistinctly]</i>

47:27.375 --> 47:30.625
<i>[Cordoza] Mrs. Stirling,</i>
<i>this just came for you.</i>

47:32.750 --> 47:33.583
<i>Thank you.</i>

47:35.750 --> 47:38.875
<i>[O'Hare] </i>Dearest J, please know
that I was not rejecting you.

47:38.958 --> 47:41.708
<i>I have never wanted</i>
<i>to kiss someone so badly,</i>

47:41.791 --> 47:43.958
<i>but when you looked up at me,</i>
<i>something changed.</i>

47:44.041 --> 47:47.416
<i>And in that moment,</i>
<i>I feared our desires would destroy us.</i>

47:47.500 --> 47:49.291
<i>You're an honest, remarkable creature,</i>

47:49.375 --> 47:53.625
<i>and I did not want to be responsible</i>
<i>for making you someone less than you are.</i>

47:53.708 --> 47:56.416
<i>For that reason,</i>
<i>I've spent the last week hating myself</i>

47:56.500 --> 47:58.583
<i>for the one decent thing I've ever done.</i>

47:59.458 --> 48:03.291
<i>So consider this. Spontaneity is</i>
<i>at the heart of many wonderful things</i>,

48:03.375 --> 48:06.125
<i>but it is also</i>
<i>at the root of much discontent.</i>

48:06.208 --> 48:08.625
<i>And if we are to embark upon something,</i>

48:08.708 --> 48:11.541
<i>I ask only that we</i>
<i>make this decision as one.</i>

48:12.666 --> 48:15.625
<i>I write these words with you in mind,</i>
<i>and my heart swells.</i>

48:16.708 --> 48:20.458
<i>So whatever the outcome,</i>
<i>let us survive together.</i>

48:21.000 --> 48:23.875
<i>You'll find me</i>
<i>at Postman's Park on Friday at 6:00 p.m.</i>

48:24.625 --> 48:25.833
<i>I'll be there waiting.</i>

48:26.375 --> 48:29.208
<i>Yours, respectfully, Boot.</i>

48:29.291 --> 48:30.125
<i>Boot.</i>

48:30.750 --> 48:32.958
<i>[romantic instrumental music playing]</i>

48:57.750 --> 49:00.541
<i>["What'cha Gone Do About It"</i>
<i>by Doris Troy playing]</i>

49:06.416 --> 49:09.916
<i>♪ Our love, yeah ♪</i>

49:12.375 --> 49:18.708
<i>♪ Is slowly going on the rocks now</i>
<i>Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah ♪</i>

49:18.791 --> 49:21.958
<i>♪ Tell me</i>
<i>Tell me, baby ♪</i>

49:23.125 --> 49:24.666
<i>♪ What'cha gonna do 'bout it ♪</i>

49:25.541 --> 49:27.750
<i>♪ What'cha gonna do 'bout it ♪</i>

49:27.833 --> 49:29.583
<i>♪ Our love, yeah ♪</i>

49:32.333 --> 49:35.875
<i>♪ Is in double jeopardy</i>… <i>♪</i>

49:35.958 --> 49:37.125
<i>Felipe!</i>

49:38.166 --> 49:39.375
<i>-How are you?</i>
<i>-Good.</i>

49:39.458 --> 49:42.666
<i>-This is Jennifer. My friend Felipe.</i>
<i>-Nice to meet you.</i>

49:43.791 --> 49:45.125
<i>How's it going? Good?</i>

49:45.250 --> 49:48.291
<i>♪ What'cha gonna do 'bout it</i>… <i>♪</i>

49:49.541 --> 49:50.791
<i>Enjoy!</i>

49:50.875 --> 49:52.458
<i>-Thank you.</i>
<i>-Thanks.</i>

49:52.541 --> 49:55.041
<i>-Cheers.</i>
<i>-Cheers.</i>

49:57.166 --> 50:02.500
<i>♪ And if you keep on doin'</i>
<i>Doin' what you're doin' ♪</i>

50:02.583 --> 50:04.666
<i>♪ You know our love will surely end</i>… <i>♪</i>

50:04.750 --> 50:05.875
<i>Same again.</i>

50:06.375 --> 50:09.416
<i>Come, Mr. Boot. Dance with me.</i>

50:09.500 --> 50:11.125
<i>[Felipe] Have fun, my friend.</i>

50:11.208 --> 50:14.291
<i>♪ Is slowly going on the rocks now ♪</i>

50:15.166 --> 50:17.000
<i>♪ Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah ♪</i>

50:17.625 --> 50:20.875
<i>♪ Tell me</i>
<i>Tell me, baby ♪</i>

50:22.125 --> 50:26.708
<i>♪ What'cha gonna do 'bout it</i>
<i>What'cha gonna do 'bout it ♪</i>

50:26.791 --> 50:30.500
<i>♪ Oh, tell me</i>
<i>Tell me, baby ♪</i>

50:31.750 --> 50:33.291
<i>♪ What'cha gonna do 'bout it ♪</i>

50:34.208 --> 50:35.958
<i>♪ What'cha gonna do 'bout it… ♪</i>

50:36.041 --> 50:37.583
<i>[both chuckle, panting]</i>

50:44.375 --> 50:46.291
<i>["Straight From The Heart"</i>
<i>by Irma Thomas playing]</i>

50:46.375 --> 50:51.583
<i>♪ Do you need me like I need you ♪</i>

50:53.083 --> 50:59.125
<i>♪ Look at me</i>
<i>I'm crying from holding you ♪</i>

51:00.916 --> 51:07.208
<i>♪ Make me forget the pain that you cause ♪</i>

51:07.958 --> 51:10.708
<i>♪ Understanding is a great thing ♪</i>

51:11.750 --> 51:13.916
<i>♪ If it comes from the heart ♪</i>

51:16.041 --> 51:21.791
<i>♪ If time would stand still</i>
<i>While I'm thinking of you ♪</i>

51:23.458 --> 51:29.541
<i>♪ I think of all the pain</i>
<i>That I wanted of you ♪</i>

51:31.291 --> 51:37.416
<i>♪ To make me forget</i>
<i>The pain that you cause ♪</i>

51:38.333 --> 51:40.875
<i>♪ Understanding is a great thing ♪</i>

51:42.250 --> 51:44.625
<i>♪ If it comes from the heart ♪</i>

51:48.375 --> 51:49.875
<i>♪ Picking up the pieces ♪</i>

51:52.000 --> 51:54.083
<i>-♪ Of my broken heart ♪</i>
-[Jenny moaning]

51:54.166 --> 51:55.416
<i>♪ It was real hard ♪</i>

51:55.500 --> 51:57.083
<i>[panting]</i>

51:59.583 --> 52:01.833
<i>♪ A fragile thing like life ♪</i>

52:03.083 --> 52:04.541
<i>♪ It just don't last so long ♪</i>

52:06.250 --> 52:08.625
<i>♪ It could be for a minute or an hour… ♪</i>

52:08.708 --> 52:13.125
<i>[Ellie] </i>"Seize this thing
that is true, and real, and infinite."

52:14.333 --> 52:17.500
<i>"Yes, it's scary,</i>
<i>but I believe that living a lie is worse."</i>

52:18.750 --> 52:21.583
<i>"We could be happy. So happy."</i>

52:21.666 --> 52:22.583
<i>[knocks at door]</i>

52:24.750 --> 52:25.583
<i>Hey.</i>

52:26.375 --> 52:28.916
<i>-You beat me to it.</i>
-<i>Yeah, I'm pretty excited.</i>

52:29.000 --> 52:32.500
<i>Yeah. Um, look, I can't make</i>
<i>any promises, though.</i>

52:33.583 --> 52:35.500
<i>Well, thanks for doing this.</i>

52:35.583 --> 52:38.875
<i>Um, before we go in,</i>
<i>you're gonna have to remove your shoes.</i>

52:40.875 --> 52:42.958
<i>-Seriously?</i>
<i>-Kidding.</i>

52:44.083 --> 52:45.333
<i>You're a funny guy.</i>

52:46.208 --> 52:48.583
<i>So this is everything</i>
<i>that's non-cataloged.</i>

52:49.916 --> 52:50.791
<i>Holy moly.</i>

52:52.500 --> 52:53.375
<i>And…</i>

52:54.708 --> 53:01.208
<i>this should be</i>
<i>all of the stuff from 1964 to 1965.</i>

53:01.291 --> 53:02.541
<i>[phone ringing]</i>

53:02.625 --> 53:03.958
<i>[Ellie] Feel free to get that.</i>

53:04.041 --> 53:07.041
<i>[phone ringing]</i>

53:07.125 --> 53:08.125
<i>[Rory] Not important.</i>

53:08.208 --> 53:09.166
<i>[call ends mid-ring]</i>

53:10.625 --> 53:12.208
<i>[Rory] Oh, um. I… I…</i>

53:12.291 --> 53:14.208
<i>-Could you give me a hand?</i>
<i>-Yeah, sure.</i>

53:18.875 --> 53:19.833
<i>[Ellie] Careful.</i>

53:23.041 --> 53:25.708
<i>-Not this stuff?</i>
<i>-[Rory] Yeah, no, not those.</i>

53:27.000 --> 53:27.833
<i>[Ellie] Um…</i>

53:28.583 --> 53:29.416
<i>[softly] Um…</i>

53:30.375 --> 53:32.458
<i>-Help you down?</i>
<i>-Great.</i>

53:35.458 --> 53:37.958
<i>-So, um…</i>
<i>-Right, should we…</i>

53:38.041 --> 53:39.833
<i>-Should we get started?</i>
<i>-Yeah. Yeah.</i>

53:40.458 --> 53:42.083
<i>Let's get started.</i>

53:42.958 --> 53:45.208
<i>["Give You What I Got"</i>
<i>by Wendy Rene playing]</i>

53:45.291 --> 53:50.500
<i>♪ Made up my mind</i>
<i>Not to quit trying… ♪</i>

53:50.583 --> 53:55.166
<i>[O'Hare] </i>My dearest J, there is no sound
sweeter than your knock on the door.

53:55.250 --> 53:57.500
<i>It's like there's always</i>
<i>a part of me waiting for it.</i>

53:57.583 --> 54:01.791
<i>I struggle to focus at work because</i>
<i>my thoughts veer irrevocably back to you.</i>

54:02.875 --> 54:05.291
<i>What do global warfare</i>
<i>and politics matter to me now?</i>

54:05.375 --> 54:06.625
<i>[doorbell rings]</i>

54:07.333 --> 54:09.833
<i>If this carries on,</i>
<i>they'll put me on the gardening pages.</i>

54:09.916 --> 54:14.541
<i>♪ Give you all the love I got ♪</i>

54:14.625 --> 54:16.416
<i>♪ Make you mine, baby ♪</i>

54:18.000 --> 54:22.500
<i>♪ I'll spend all my time</i>… <i>♪</i>

54:26.833 --> 54:28.000
<i>[Jenny chuckles]</i>

54:30.125 --> 54:31.375
<i>[O'Hare] Close your eyes.</i>

54:31.875 --> 54:33.916
<i>[Jenny] The shadow's</i>
<i>at the foot of the bed, Mr. Boot.</i>

54:34.000 --> 54:37.583
<i>[O'Hare] What terrible thing will happen</i>
<i>if you stayed beyond five o'clock?</i>

54:37.666 --> 54:39.625
<i>[Jenny] I'll stay</i>
<i>until it reaches my knees.</i>

54:39.750 --> 54:41.125
<i>-Waist.</i>
<i>-Knees.</i>

54:41.791 --> 54:42.666
<i>Deal.</i>

54:43.750 --> 54:44.583
<i>Eyes.</i>

54:45.666 --> 54:46.541
<i>[sighs]</i>

54:47.583 --> 54:48.416
<i>Close them.</i>

54:50.000 --> 54:51.000
<i>[softly] Close them.</i>

54:51.791 --> 54:52.666
<i>[Jenny chuckles]</i>

54:55.750 --> 54:56.583
<i>[O'Hare sighs]</i>

54:57.625 --> 55:01.458
<i>Canvas tent</i>
<i>in the middle of the wilderness.</i>

55:02.000 --> 55:05.458
<i>[sighs deeply] If you insist.</i>

55:06.750 --> 55:11.750
<i>We sleep on a bed of leaves,</i>
<i>bathe in a nearby river.</i>

55:11.833 --> 55:13.666
<i>[soft instrumental music playing]</i>

55:13.750 --> 55:15.125
<i>And when the sun goes down…</i>

55:16.458 --> 55:17.916
<i>[softly] …we build a fire.</i>

55:18.416 --> 55:19.250
<i>Hmm.</i>

55:19.916 --> 55:22.416
<i>Thank goodness because I'm ravenous.</i>

55:23.291 --> 55:25.750
<i>-What are we having?</i>
<i>-Wild fruit.</i>

55:33.791 --> 55:34.625
<i>Namely?</i>

55:36.458 --> 55:39.625
<i>[softly] Elderberries. Blackberries.</i>

55:43.375 --> 55:44.750
<i>Maybe some dandelion.</i>

55:58.250 --> 55:59.333
<i>[softly] Perfect.</i>

56:32.541 --> 56:33.458
<i>[Jenny] Mmm.</i>

56:33.541 --> 56:35.291
<i>[softly] Good night, dear Boot.</i>

56:41.208 --> 56:42.125
<i>[Jenny scoffs]</i>

56:47.791 --> 56:48.625
<i>[chuckles] What?</i>

56:49.416 --> 56:50.250
<i>What is it?</i>

56:52.250 --> 56:53.416
<i>I don't want you to go.</i>

56:53.500 --> 56:54.791
<i>[Jenny chuckles]</i>

56:56.541 --> 56:58.250
<i>What if we ran away together?</i>

56:59.125 --> 56:59.958
<i>To where?</i>

57:01.416 --> 57:03.625
<i>-How about New York?</i>
<i>-Hmm.</i>

57:04.625 --> 57:06.166
<i>[softly] I love New York.</i>

57:09.125 --> 57:10.500
<i>I've been offered a post there.</i>

57:12.625 --> 57:14.333
<i>And I want you to come with me.</i>

57:19.958 --> 57:20.791
<i>Hmm.</i>

57:23.833 --> 57:25.083
<i>Move to New York with me.</i>

57:26.583 --> 57:28.791
<i>-You know I can't.</i>
<i>-Yes, you can.</i>

57:28.875 --> 57:30.333
<i>Yes, you can. We can.</i>

57:31.916 --> 57:37.000
<i>You're just asking me to run away,</i>
<i>to just give up my life?</i>

57:37.083 --> 57:39.875
<i>Well, in order to start a new one, yes.</i>

57:39.958 --> 57:43.958
<i>-[scoffs] And when you grow tired of me?</i>
<i>-That won't happen.</i>

57:44.041 --> 57:47.416
<i>-It has before. What makes this different?</i>
<i>-What makes-- Everything.</i>

57:48.708 --> 57:50.500
<i>Everything about this is different.</i>

57:52.875 --> 57:56.625
<i>If you think that this is even close</i>
<i>to anything that I've ever felt before,</i>

57:57.500 --> 58:00.500
<i>ever known,</i>
<i>then you couldn't be more wrong.</i>

58:02.750 --> 58:05.291
<i>[softly] Jennifer, I love you.</i>

58:05.375 --> 58:07.791
<i>I'm in love with you,</i>
<i>and I want to share my life with you.</i>

58:07.875 --> 58:10.708
<i>You're in love with the idea of it all</i>
<i>and you're being impulsive.</i>

58:10.791 --> 58:12.875
<i>-And I don't like it.</i>
<i>-[sternly] I'm being instinctive!</i>

58:12.958 --> 58:15.208
<i>Do you have any idea</i>
<i>what you're asking of me?</i>

58:16.375 --> 58:18.458
<i>My family, my friends,</i>
<i>they would disown me.</i>

58:18.541 --> 58:20.791
<i>All the more reason to leave them behind.</i>

58:21.541 --> 58:24.375
<i>-[scoffs] So easy for you.</i>
<i>-Easy?</i>

58:24.458 --> 58:27.208
<i>Watching you return home</i>
<i>every night to a man who--</i>

58:27.291 --> 58:28.250
<i>A man who what?</i>

58:30.583 --> 58:34.625
<i>I think it's entirely possible that</i>
<i>you might be wasted in the life you're in.</i>

58:34.708 --> 58:36.875
<i>[dramatic music playing]</i>

58:55.000 --> 58:58.958
<i>[Jenny] </i>Boot, it's true. I was brought up
to do what is expected of me

58:59.041 --> 59:01.333
<i>rather than what might make me happy.</i>

59:01.416 --> 59:02.916
<i>I'm afraid to love you.</i>

59:03.000 --> 59:07.458
<i>I'm afraid that if I let myself go,</i>
<i>I'd love you so much it would consume me.</i>

59:07.541 --> 59:11.041
<i>And I fear that once I cease to be</i>
<i>a novelty, you might tire of me.</i>

59:12.125 --> 59:14.458
<i>You have to understand</i>
<i>that if I were to leave with you,</i>

59:14.541 --> 59:17.333
<i>it's not just my family</i>
<i>and my security I would lose.</i>

59:17.416 --> 59:19.000
<i>It's my very peace of mind.</i>

59:19.875 --> 59:22.708
<i>And it's a risk I don't think</i>
<i>I'm strong enough to take.</i>

59:23.333 --> 59:26.833
<i>I hope you understand. Yours always, J.</i>

59:29.166 --> 59:30.916
<i>[O'Hare] </i>My dearest and only love,

59:32.083 --> 59:33.250
<i>I know you're frightened,</i>

59:33.333 --> 59:36.583
<i>but believe me when I say</i>
<i>I've known nothing like this before</i>

59:36.666 --> 59:39.291
<i>and can assure you</i>
<i>that I never will again.</i>

59:39.791 --> 59:42.791
<i>It's with that certainty that</i>
<i>I've decided to make a bold decision.</i>

59:42.875 --> 59:45.250
<i>I'm going to take the job in New York.</i>

59:45.333 --> 59:49.291
<i>I'll be on platform two,</i>
<i>Marylebone, Friday at 7:15 p.m.</i>

59:49.375 --> 59:50.583
<i>Come with me, darling.</i>

59:51.083 --> 59:54.333
<i>Spare him a life half-lived,</i>
<i>a marriage of convenience.</i>

59:54.416 --> 59:56.583
<i>More importantly, spare yourself.</i>

59:56.666 --> 59:59.541
<i>Seize this thing</i>
<i>that is true and real and infinite.</i>

1:00:00.125 --> 1:00:03.583
<i>Yes, it is scary,</i>
<i>but I believe living a lie is worse.</i>

1:00:10.458 --> 1:00:14.375
<i>[Cordoza] A call from Mr. Stirling's</i>
<i>office. He says to go ahead without him.</i>

1:00:17.791 --> 1:00:20.250
<i>[O'Hare] </i>We could be happy. So happy.

1:00:21.166 --> 1:00:26.500
<i>Know that you hold my hopes,</i>
<i>my heart in your hands. Your Boot.</i>

1:00:26.583 --> 1:00:28.208
<i>[ticking]</i>

1:00:40.583 --> 1:00:42.583
<i>[suspenseful instrumental music playing]</i>

1:00:51.041 --> 1:00:51.916
<i>[yells] Taxi!</i>

1:00:55.458 --> 1:00:56.666
<i>[man yells] Make way!</i>

1:00:57.708 --> 1:00:58.958
<i>[whistle blows]</i>

1:01:22.000 --> 1:01:24.666
<i>-Felipe, you think we'll make it in time?</i>
<i>-I think so.</i>

1:01:25.750 --> 1:01:26.875
<i>Just barely.</i>

1:01:42.916 --> 1:01:45.458
<i>-[train whistle blows]</i>
<i>-[man yells] Coming through!</i>

1:01:50.541 --> 1:01:51.958
<i>Felipe, please hurry.</i>

1:02:05.333 --> 1:02:07.125
<i>[man yells] All aboard!</i>

1:02:20.375 --> 1:02:21.708
<i>-[horn blaring]</i>
<i>-[braking]</i>

1:02:21.791 --> 1:02:24.416
<i>-[gasps]</i>
<i>-[train whistle blows]</i>

1:02:28.708 --> 1:02:30.708
<i>[somber instrumental music playing]</i>

1:02:56.500 --> 1:02:57.750
<i>[ambulance wails in distance]</i>

1:02:57.833 --> 1:03:00.541
<i>[Ellie] "Our famous heavyweight</i>
<i>corduroy trousers,</i>

1:03:00.625 --> 1:03:03.833
<i>rubber shirt-grip waistband,</i>
<i>elastic side straps,</i>

1:03:03.916 --> 1:03:05.708
<i>three roomy pockets…"</i>

1:03:05.791 --> 1:03:09.000
<i>[phone rings]</i>

1:03:09.083 --> 1:03:11.666
<i>-[Ellie] It's cool if you wanna get that.</i>
<i>-[Rory] No.</i>

1:03:12.583 --> 1:03:18.541
<i>[Ellie] "Uh, available in brown,</i>
<i>fawn, bottle green, and gray."</i>

1:03:19.583 --> 1:03:22.166
<i>"Authentic detailing</i>
<i>and rugged tailoring."</i>

1:03:22.250 --> 1:03:23.250
<i>Very fine indeed.</i>

1:03:24.666 --> 1:03:26.000
<i>Ah. "Mega-Mash."</i>

1:03:26.916 --> 1:03:30.291
<i>-"Smashingly smooth, fluffy, flavorsome."</i>
<i>-[Rory] Ellie.</i>

1:03:33.083 --> 1:03:34.916
<i>-I think I found one.</i>
<i>-Oh my God!</i>

1:03:36.708 --> 1:03:38.041
<i>Read it out!</i>

1:03:40.291 --> 1:03:41.291
<i>"Dearest J,</i>

1:03:42.000 --> 1:03:46.416
<i>I've spent my life avoiding complication,</i>
<i>especially the romantic kind."</i>

1:03:46.500 --> 1:03:50.583
<i>"Having met you, I now realize that what</i>
<i>I was doing wasn't really living at all."</i>

1:03:51.041 --> 1:03:54.875
<i>"I know it's hard for you to hear that</i>
<i>I love you, but I have to say the words."</i>

1:03:54.958 --> 1:03:58.208
<i>"They're in my head from the moment</i>
<i>I wake until I fall asleep again,</i>

1:03:58.708 --> 1:04:02.291
<i>and if I can't say them,</i>
<i>I'll write them to you again and again."</i>

1:04:03.458 --> 1:04:05.541
<i>"I love you, dear Jenny. Your B."</i>

1:04:06.625 --> 1:04:07.541
<i>Shit.</i>

1:04:08.875 --> 1:04:12.291
<i>We should just check out the PO box</i>
<i>the other letters were sent to</i>

1:04:12.375 --> 1:04:13.625
<i>and see if it still exists.</i>

1:04:13.708 --> 1:04:14.791
<i>Yes!</i>

1:04:14.875 --> 1:04:16.333
<i>[phone ringing]</i>

1:04:19.083 --> 1:04:20.958
<i>[Rory chuckles] What are you doing?</i>

1:04:21.041 --> 1:04:23.250
<i>Rory's phone. Ellie speaking.</i>

1:04:24.000 --> 1:04:27.458
<i>Uh… we work together.</i>
<i>I'm afraid I made him stay late.</i>

1:04:27.541 --> 1:04:29.208
<i>[both mouthing silently]</i>

1:04:30.750 --> 1:04:31.583
<i>Uh…</i>

1:04:32.166 --> 1:04:35.625
<i>No. No, no, no, no, no, no.</i>
<i>I'm… I'm sorry.</i>

1:04:36.125 --> 1:04:38.458
<i>[chuckles] Okay. Okay. See you.</i>

1:04:40.500 --> 1:04:42.541
<i>Why didn't you tell me it's your birthday?</i>

1:04:43.291 --> 1:04:46.708
<i>I… I would rather be doing this.</i>

1:04:49.125 --> 1:04:51.458
<i>Right. Get your stuff together.</i>

1:04:51.541 --> 1:04:53.791
<i>[upbeat pop music playing]</i>

1:04:53.875 --> 1:04:56.750
<i>So why would you invite</i>
<i>your ex to your birthday party?</i>

1:04:59.375 --> 1:05:02.750
<i>I didn't. I had no idea</i>
<i>she was gonna be here.</i>

1:05:02.833 --> 1:05:04.333
<i>Well, who invited her, then?</i>

1:05:04.416 --> 1:05:08.208
<i>She's my sister's friend, and</i>
<i>I'm not talking to any of them tonight.</i>

1:05:08.291 --> 1:05:11.458
<i>-[Ellie] So what happened with you guys?</i>
<i>-[Rory] She was religious.</i>

1:05:11.541 --> 1:05:15.375
<i>But I guess when we met,</i>
<i>she was only a bit religious.</i>

1:05:15.458 --> 1:05:17.416
<i>And as the relationship</i>
<i>went on, she was like,</i>

1:05:17.500 --> 1:05:21.625
<i>"Actually, the fact you don't believe</i>
<i>in God is a deal breaker for me."</i>

1:05:22.625 --> 1:05:25.833
<i>But, in the end, she married this guy.</i>

1:05:27.458 --> 1:05:29.791
<i>You know. You win some, you lose some.</i>

1:05:32.166 --> 1:05:33.000
<i>What about you?</i>

1:05:33.083 --> 1:05:34.166
<i>[scoffs]</i>

1:05:34.250 --> 1:05:37.833
<i>-You don't wanna know about me.</i>
<i>-You couldn't be more wrong.</i>

1:05:39.958 --> 1:05:41.916
<i>Well, I was with someone for a while.</i>

1:05:42.000 --> 1:05:42.833
<i>Define a while.</i>

1:05:43.583 --> 1:05:48.166
<i>Eight years.</i>
<i>And he really wanted kids, but I didn't.</i>

1:05:49.125 --> 1:05:51.416
<i>So… so we broke up.</i>

1:05:53.166 --> 1:05:54.000
<i>I'm sorry.</i>

1:05:54.083 --> 1:05:57.500
<i>That isn't even the end. Then we got</i>
<i>back together and then broke up again.</i>

1:05:57.583 --> 1:06:01.125
<i>Then there was this whole awful</i>
<i>smorgasbord of haphazard shagging.</i>

1:06:01.208 --> 1:06:02.708
<i>And then finally, he proposed.</i>

1:06:03.208 --> 1:06:07.375
<i>Uh, we were on holiday with about</i>
<i>a dozen of our nearest and dearest.</i>

1:06:07.458 --> 1:06:08.416
<i>Oh gosh.</i>

1:06:10.333 --> 1:06:11.333
<i>Yep.</i>

1:06:12.166 --> 1:06:14.833
<i>I mean, it wasn't even</i>
<i>that I didn't love him. I just…</i>

1:06:15.750 --> 1:06:17.875
<i>I just wasn't sure</i>
<i>that I loved him enough.</i>

1:06:18.791 --> 1:06:20.541
<i>Maybe I do want kids. I don't know.</i>

1:06:21.333 --> 1:06:25.000
<i>But pretty much knew for sure</i>
<i>I didn't want them with him.</i>

1:06:25.750 --> 1:06:30.083
<i>Well, that sounds like</i>
<i>a really shit breakup. I'm sorry.</i>

1:06:30.166 --> 1:06:34.083
<i>And that is why people shouldn't talk</i>
<i>about themselves, 'cause it's depressing.</i>

1:06:34.833 --> 1:06:36.416
<i>Yeah, it's really depressing.</i>

1:06:36.500 --> 1:06:39.375
<i>I think it might be time</i>
<i>for your birthday dance.</i>

1:06:40.041 --> 1:06:41.416
<i>My birthday dance?</i>

1:06:41.500 --> 1:06:43.083
<i>Yes. Your birthday dance.</i>

1:06:43.166 --> 1:06:46.625
<i>["Ain't Love Good,</i>
<i>Ain't Love Proud" playing]</i>

1:06:46.708 --> 1:06:50.125
<i>♪ And I'm gonna tell each and every one</i>
<i>Of you to give me some assistance now ♪</i>

1:06:50.208 --> 1:06:52.833
<i>♪ Ain't love good</i>
<i>Ain't love proud ♪</i>

1:06:52.916 --> 1:06:55.541
<i>♪ Ain't love good</i>
<i>Ain't love proud ♪</i>

1:06:55.625 --> 1:06:57.166
<i>♪ Let me hear the music ♪</i>

1:06:58.208 --> 1:07:02.291
<i>♪ All right</i>
<i>All right ♪</i>

1:07:03.416 --> 1:07:04.500
<i>♪ Well, listen, child ♪</i>

1:07:05.916 --> 1:07:11.125
<i>♪ Don't ya know it's a big, bright world</i>
<i>When a guy meets a girl ♪</i>

1:07:11.208 --> 1:07:16.625
<i>♪ Don't ya know if the girl is real</i>
<i>Well then it's got to be so sweet ♪</i>

1:07:16.708 --> 1:07:22.583
<i>♪ Don't ya know it's a good, good feeling</i>
<i>That sends your heart a-reelin' ♪</i>

1:07:22.666 --> 1:07:27.708
<i>♪ Everybody now clap your hands, children</i>
<i>Stomp them feet ♪</i>

1:07:27.791 --> 1:07:29.291
<i>[Ellie] Oh, cool flat.</i>

1:07:30.000 --> 1:07:32.541
<i>Yeah, this is, uh… this is me.</i>

1:07:32.625 --> 1:07:34.000
<i>[both chuckle]</i>

1:07:34.083 --> 1:07:36.291
<i>[Ellie] It's nice! Oh your cat!</i>

1:07:36.375 --> 1:07:37.208
<i>[Rory] Diesel.</i>

1:07:37.666 --> 1:07:38.625
<i>[Ellie] Hi, Diesel.</i>

1:07:39.958 --> 1:07:41.000
<i>[meows]</i>

1:07:41.375 --> 1:07:42.333
<i>[Rory] Refreshment?</i>

1:07:42.916 --> 1:07:45.750
<i>[Ellie] Yeah. Uh…</i>
<i>maybe, actually, water.</i>

1:07:46.166 --> 1:07:47.000
<i>[Rory] Yeah.</i>

1:07:47.083 --> 1:07:48.083
<i>[Ellie] Thanks.</i>

1:07:55.666 --> 1:07:57.083
<i>So many records.</i>

1:07:57.958 --> 1:07:59.166
<i>It's kinda hobby of mine.</i>

1:07:59.958 --> 1:08:02.583
<i>["Love to Know" by Marine Girls playing]</i>

1:08:04.375 --> 1:08:05.208
<i>Hello.</i>

1:08:05.708 --> 1:08:10.250
<i>♪ Hello Marc</i>
<i>Long time no see ♪</i>

1:08:10.333 --> 1:08:14.375
<i>♪ I bet you don't remember me</i>… <i>♪</i>

1:08:15.375 --> 1:08:16.583
<i>[Ellie] So these, um…</i>

1:08:17.958 --> 1:08:19.333
<i>these ladies…</i>

1:08:20.458 --> 1:08:21.916
<i>they're all your sisters, right?</i>

1:08:22.000 --> 1:08:24.833
<i>Uh, no, uh,</i>
<i>I'm a serial bigamist, actually.</i>

1:08:24.916 --> 1:08:25.833
<i>Oh.</i>

1:08:26.583 --> 1:08:29.083
<i>Yeah. Shucks, I thought so.</i>

1:08:29.166 --> 1:08:30.250
<i>[chuckles]</i>

1:08:34.583 --> 1:08:37.666
<i>♪ By the way, have you seen him lately</i>? <i>♪</i>

1:08:39.833 --> 1:08:46.833
<i>♪ Could you tell me how is he? ♪</i>

1:08:55.083 --> 1:08:59.458
<i>♪ I haven't seen him for so long ♪</i>

1:08:59.541 --> 1:09:03.541
<i>♪ Don't think of him when I'm alone ♪</i>

1:09:04.291 --> 1:09:08.208
<i>♪ Time flies so fast doing this alone ♪</i>

1:09:09.375 --> 1:09:14.750
<i>♪ It was two years the other night</i>
<i>And I forgot ♪</i>

1:10:05.583 --> 1:10:06.416
<i>[opens creakily]</i>

1:10:32.916 --> 1:10:34.875
<i>[phone vibrates]</i>

1:10:38.541 --> 1:10:39.416
<i>[softly] Oh shit.</i>

1:10:45.250 --> 1:10:47.250
<i>Hi. Um…</i>

1:10:47.916 --> 1:10:50.791
<i>-I was wondering--</i>
<i>-Sorry, you're gonna have to speak up.</i>

1:10:50.875 --> 1:10:54.958
<i>[louder] Oh, um, how do I find out</i>
<i>who owns one of these PO boxes?</i>

1:10:55.041 --> 1:10:57.125
<i>[woman] You want to open a PO box?</i>

1:10:57.208 --> 1:11:00.500
<i>No, no, I want to find out</i>
<i>who owns one of them.</i>

1:11:00.583 --> 1:11:02.250
<i>Are you the owner of the box?</i>

1:11:02.875 --> 1:11:07.083
<i>No, I… I want to find out who owns</i>
<i>one of them so I can write to them.</i>

1:11:07.208 --> 1:11:09.458
<i>I mean, I want to find out</i>
<i>if they still own it,</i>

1:11:09.541 --> 1:11:11.958
<i>if you, uh… if you see what I'm saying.</i>

1:11:12.041 --> 1:11:16.250
<i>You've obviously not heard of that</i>
<i>little thing called "data protection."</i>

1:11:17.541 --> 1:11:18.708
<i>You know what, um?</i>

1:11:19.833 --> 1:11:22.916
<i>Don't worry about it.</i>
<i>I will, uh… I'll figure something out.</i>

1:11:27.250 --> 1:11:29.250
<i>[soft instrumental music playing]</i>

1:11:38.083 --> 1:11:39.041
<i>[Ellie] </i>Dear J,

1:11:39.125 --> 1:11:42.250
<i>this might sound strange, but I found</i>
<i>some letters that may belong to you,</i>

1:11:42.333 --> 1:11:46.041
<i>addressed to JS, postmark 1965.</i>

1:11:46.125 --> 1:11:48.458
<i>They appear to be of sentimental value.</i>

1:11:48.541 --> 1:11:50.958
<i>If you could bare to tell me,</i>
<i>I'd love to know the story</i>

1:11:51.041 --> 1:11:52.750
<i>behind them and Mr. Boot.</i>

1:11:52.833 --> 1:11:54.791
<i>With all best wishes, Ellie Haworth.</i>

1:12:06.291 --> 1:12:09.500
<i>[Ellie] </i>"Dear Miss Haworth, I do not wish
to speak to you regarding the events

1:12:09.583 --> 1:12:11.916
<i>of the period</i>
<i>outlined to me in your letter,</i>

1:12:12.000 --> 1:12:15.791
<i>and as such will be unable to assist you</i>
<i>any further with your investigation."</i>

1:12:15.875 --> 1:12:17.916
<i>"Sincerely, Jennifer Stirling."</i>

1:12:18.000 --> 1:12:20.125
<i>[inspirational instrumental music playing]</i>

1:12:26.375 --> 1:12:27.500
<i>Okay, I'll see you.</i>

1:12:28.500 --> 1:12:30.208
<i>-Bye.</i>
<i>-Bye.</i>

1:12:50.708 --> 1:12:51.791
<i>[buzzes]</i>

1:12:57.083 --> 1:12:57.916
<i>[woman] Hello?</i>

1:12:58.916 --> 1:13:00.583
<i>Is that… is that Mrs. Stirling?</i>

1:13:01.166 --> 1:13:02.291
<i>[Jenny] </i>Speaking.

1:13:02.375 --> 1:13:06.166
<i>Hello, hi. I'm, um… I'm Ellie Haworth</i>
<i>from </i>The London Chronicle<i>.</i>

1:13:06.250 --> 1:13:10.166
<i>I… I wrote to you regarding a series</i>
<i>of letters that myself and my colleague--</i>

1:13:10.250 --> 1:13:13.458
<i>[Jenny] </i>Yes, yes, and I have responded
via the enclosed address.

1:13:14.291 --> 1:13:15.416
<i>Yes, um…</i>

1:13:15.500 --> 1:13:17.583
<i>I… I just…</i>

1:13:17.666 --> 1:13:21.000
<i>Look, um, if now is inconvenient,</i>
<i>I'm… I'm more than happy--</i>

1:13:21.083 --> 1:13:23.000
<i>[Jenny] </i>I'm sorry,
but as I said in my letter,

1:13:23.083 --> 1:13:26.333
<i>what happened between myself</i>
<i>and Mr. O'Hare is a private matter.</i>

1:13:29.708 --> 1:13:33.791
<i>Yes, of course,</i>
<i>and I'm… I'm very sorry for intruding.</i>

1:13:33.875 --> 1:13:37.333
<i>Um. I just wanted</i>
<i>at the very least to return--</i>

1:13:37.416 --> 1:13:38.458
<i>[intercom hangs up]</i>

1:13:39.416 --> 1:13:40.250
<i>Hello?</i>

1:13:42.083 --> 1:13:42.958
<i>[in singsong] Hello?</i>

1:13:45.958 --> 1:13:46.791
<i>Shit.</i>

1:14:03.083 --> 1:14:05.083
<i>[dramatic instrumental music playing]</i>

1:14:21.416 --> 1:14:25.000
<i>Mrs. Stirling, lovely to see you again.</i>
<i>We've missed you.</i>

1:14:28.541 --> 1:14:31.458
<i>Yes, it's… it's lovely to see you too.</i>

1:14:33.458 --> 1:14:37.041
<i>I wouldn't suppose you have a spare key?</i>
<i>I seemed to have left mine at home.</i>

1:14:37.125 --> 1:14:40.291
<i>Certainly, ma'am,</i>
<i>but PO box 13 is no longer in service.</i>

1:14:41.166 --> 1:14:42.000
<i>I'm sorry?</i>

1:14:42.708 --> 1:14:47.041
<i>As per Mr. Stirling's request,</i>
<i>it's been closed for the last month.</i>

1:14:48.791 --> 1:14:52.125
<i>[sternly] Well, reopen it now. Please.</i>

1:14:52.208 --> 1:14:53.458
<i>[woman] Certainly, ma'am.</i>

1:14:54.666 --> 1:14:57.250
<i>Mrs. Cordoza, I need the keys</i>
<i>to my husband's study.</i>

1:14:57.750 --> 1:15:00.333
<i>I'm afraid this is an instruction</i>
<i>and not a request.</i>

1:15:01.250 --> 1:15:02.083
<i>Of course.</i>

1:15:04.541 --> 1:15:05.375
<i>Thank you.</i>

1:15:06.500 --> 1:15:08.500
<i>[suspenseful instrumental music playing]</i>

1:15:42.583 --> 1:15:44.375
<i>[O'Hare] </i>My dearest and only love,

1:15:44.916 --> 1:15:46.041
<i>I know you're frightened,</i>

1:15:46.125 --> 1:15:49.458
<i>but believe me when I say</i>
<i>I've known nothing like this before</i>

1:15:49.541 --> 1:15:51.583
<i>and can assure you I never will again.</i>

1:15:51.666 --> 1:15:54.500
<i>I'll be on platform two, Marylebone, 7:15.</i>

1:15:54.583 --> 1:15:57.250
<i>Seize this thing</i>
<i>that is true and real and infinite.</i>

1:15:57.333 --> 1:15:59.125
<i>More importantly, spare yourself.</i>

1:15:59.208 --> 1:16:00.750
<i>Living a lie is worse.</i>

1:16:00.833 --> 1:16:03.166
<i>I'll never be satisfied</i>
<i>with just a part of you.</i>

1:16:03.250 --> 1:16:05.875
<i>-[Jenny] </i>It's my very peace of mind.
-<i>[O'Hare]</i> Come with me, darling.

1:16:05.958 --> 1:16:08.708
<i>-We could be happy. So happy.</i>
<i>-</i>[Jenny] <i>I would love you so much.</i>

1:16:09.458 --> 1:16:11.958
<i>[car approaching]</i>

1:16:13.541 --> 1:16:14.458
<i>[car door closes]</i>

1:16:14.916 --> 1:16:17.625
<i>[O'Hare] </i>Know that you hold my hopes,
my heart in your hands.

1:16:17.708 --> 1:16:20.125
<i>-[Jenny]</i>Yours always, J.
<i>-[O'Hare] </i>Your Boot.

1:16:34.500 --> 1:16:35.916
<i>What are you doing with this?</i>

1:16:39.750 --> 1:16:41.875
<i>Larry, why have you been tampering</i>
<i>with my mail?</i>

1:16:45.958 --> 1:16:46.916
<i>They, um…</i>

1:16:48.083 --> 1:16:52.291
<i>They found it on you…</i>
<i>the day of the accident.</i>

1:16:56.625 --> 1:16:58.125
<i>I'm guessing you know who wrote it.</i>

1:16:59.583 --> 1:17:00.458
<i>Yes.</i>

1:17:03.541 --> 1:17:06.083
<i>Yes, his name is Anthony O'Hare.</i>

1:17:08.000 --> 1:17:09.125
<i>Was.</i>

1:17:10.833 --> 1:17:11.666
<i>A journalist.</i>

1:17:13.541 --> 1:17:14.625
<i>I introduced you.</i>

1:17:17.000 --> 1:17:20.500
<i>The two of you, it seems,</i>
<i>were engaged in some kind of…</i>

1:17:25.541 --> 1:17:26.708
<i>Jenny, he was killed.</i>

1:17:27.333 --> 1:17:29.333
<i>[somber instrumental music playing]</i>

1:17:33.291 --> 1:17:34.125
<i>Wait.</i>

1:17:34.958 --> 1:17:36.875
<i>-[Larry] He was beside you in the car.</i>
<i>-No.</i>

1:17:38.916 --> 1:17:39.750
<i>No.</i>

1:17:40.250 --> 1:17:42.041
<i>The man beside me</i>
<i>in the car was named Felipe.</i>

1:17:42.125 --> 1:17:46.208
<i>The driver was Felipe, but the man in the</i>
<i>passenger seat was a Mr. Anthony O'Hare.</i>

1:17:49.833 --> 1:17:53.291
<i>And when you woke</i>
<i>from your accident, I made a decision.</i>

1:17:56.125 --> 1:17:57.541
<i>I was trying to protect you.</i>

1:17:59.458 --> 1:18:00.666
<i>-From what?</i>
<i>-The truth.</i>

1:18:02.500 --> 1:18:04.458
<i>I didn't want you</i>
<i>to have to bear the guilt.</i>

1:18:07.333 --> 1:18:09.416
<i>[footsteps leaving]</i>

1:18:12.875 --> 1:18:14.875
<i>[typing]</i>

1:18:20.041 --> 1:18:21.625
<i>[clicking]</i>

1:18:25.875 --> 1:18:27.416
<i>Holy shit.</i>

1:18:29.666 --> 1:18:31.791
<i>Anthony worked at </i>The Chronicle<i>.</i>

1:18:32.583 --> 1:18:33.541
<i>Yes.</i>

1:18:35.125 --> 1:18:36.125
<i>[typing]</i>

1:18:40.541 --> 1:18:42.250
<i>[phone vibrates]</i>

1:18:44.333 --> 1:18:46.083
<i>[soft instrumental music playing]</i>

1:18:53.541 --> 1:18:54.791
<i>[message whooshes]</i>

1:19:20.666 --> 1:19:22.666
<i>[typing]</i>

1:19:28.583 --> 1:19:29.791
<i>[email whooshes]</i>

1:19:29.875 --> 1:19:31.916
<i>[upbeat instrumental music playing]</i>

1:19:32.041 --> 1:19:33.375
<i>[sighs]</i>

1:20:04.333 --> 1:20:07.291
<i>[phone ringing]</i>

1:20:10.541 --> 1:20:11.375
<i>[groans]</i>

1:20:15.250 --> 1:20:16.958
<i>-Hello?</i>
<i>-[man] </i>Ellie Haworth?

1:20:17.041 --> 1:20:19.166
<i>-Uh-huh.</i>
<i>-[man] </i>This is Anthony O'Hare.

1:20:20.625 --> 1:20:23.000
<i>Oh. Um. [clears throat] Hi!</i>

1:20:23.625 --> 1:20:24.458
<i>Um.</i>

1:20:24.541 --> 1:20:26.291
<i>[O'Hare] </i>I believe you
wish to speak with me.

1:20:26.375 --> 1:20:27.208
<i>Yes.</i>

1:20:27.875 --> 1:20:29.875
<i>Uh, hello, Mr. O'Hare.</i>

1:20:29.958 --> 1:20:32.291
<i>So, how did you stumble on my story?</i>

1:20:33.666 --> 1:20:35.958
<i>Well, initially, I was just…</i>

1:20:36.041 --> 1:20:38.083
<i>I was just following an instinct, and…</i>

1:20:39.333 --> 1:20:42.541
<i>well, then I thought</i>
<i>there might be a feature in it. [chuckles]</i>

1:20:43.166 --> 1:20:46.416
<i>And then the more I read,</i>

1:20:47.416 --> 1:20:49.250
<i>the more I started to feel…</i>

1:20:51.375 --> 1:20:54.750
<i>I just… I found them incredibly moving.</i>

1:20:57.791 --> 1:21:00.291
<i>So, did she meet you?</i>

1:21:02.041 --> 1:21:07.583
<i>D-- Did you go to New York together?</i>

1:21:07.666 --> 1:21:08.500
<i>No.</i>

1:21:09.458 --> 1:21:12.000
<i>Mrs. Stirling</i>
<i>did not accompany me to New York.</i>

1:21:15.000 --> 1:21:16.750
<i>And was that the last-- I… I mean…</i>

1:21:18.541 --> 1:21:19.375
<i>Did you…</i>

1:21:22.166 --> 1:21:23.708
<i>Did you ever see each other again?</i>

1:21:30.291 --> 1:21:32.291
<i>["Carols of the Bells" playing]</i>

1:21:33.000 --> 1:21:35.500
<i>♪ Christmas is here</i>
<i>Bringing good cheer ♪</i>

1:21:35.583 --> 1:21:38.000
<i>♪ To young and old</i>
<i>Meek and the bold ♪</i>

1:21:38.083 --> 1:21:40.125
<i>♪ Ding-dong, ding-dong</i>
<i>That is the song ♪</i>

1:21:40.208 --> 1:21:42.750
<i>♪ With joyful ring</i>
<i>All caroling ♪</i>

1:21:42.833 --> 1:21:45.083
<i>♪ One seems to hear</i>
<i>Words of good cheer ♪</i>

1:21:45.166 --> 1:21:47.500
<i>♪ From everywhere</i>
<i>Filling the air ♪</i>

1:21:47.583 --> 1:21:49.875
<i>♪ Oh, how they pound</i>
<i>Raising their sound ♪</i>

1:21:49.958 --> 1:21:52.250
<i>♪ O'er hill and dale</i>
<i>Telling their tale ♪</i>

1:21:52.333 --> 1:21:55.791
<i>♪ Gaily they ring</i>
<i>While people sing songs of good cheer ♪</i>

1:21:55.875 --> 1:21:59.541
<i>♪ Christmas is here</i>
<i>Merry, merry, merry, merry Christmas ♪</i>

1:21:59.625 --> 1:22:01.666
<i>♪ Merry, merry, merry, merry Christmas ♪</i>

1:22:01.750 --> 1:22:04.083
<i>♪ On, on they send</i>
<i>On without end ♪</i>

1:22:04.166 --> 1:22:06.291
<i>♪ Their joyful tone</i>
<i>To every home</i>… <i>♪</i>

1:22:06.750 --> 1:22:09.916
<i>-[gasps]</i>
<i>-[O'Hare whispers] Jennifer.</i>

1:22:10.000 --> 1:22:11.708
<i>♪ Throw cares away</i>
<i>Christmas is here ♪</i>

1:22:11.791 --> 1:22:12.708
<i>[whispers] Jennifer.</i>

1:22:12.791 --> 1:22:16.416
<i>♪ To young and old</i>
<i>Meek and the bold ♪</i>

1:22:16.500 --> 1:22:18.375
<i>♪ Ding-dong, ding-dong</i>
<i>That is the song ♪</i>

1:22:18.458 --> 1:22:21.500
<i>Am I really that much</i>
<i>of a fright after all these years?</i>

1:22:21.583 --> 1:22:24.250
<i>♪ Words of good cheer</i>
<i>From everywhere ♪</i>

1:22:24.333 --> 1:22:26.500
<i>♪ Filling the air</i>
<i>Oh, how they pound</i>… ♪

1:22:27.500 --> 1:22:29.416
<i>-[softly] Can we go somewhere?</i>
<i>-Of course.</i>

1:22:29.500 --> 1:22:33.833
<i>♪ Gaily they ring</i>
<i>While people sing songs of good cheer ♪</i>

1:22:33.916 --> 1:22:37.083
<i>♪ Christmas is here</i>
<i>Merry, merry, merry, merry Christmas ♪</i>

1:22:37.166 --> 1:22:39.583
<i>♪ Merry, merry, merry, merry Christmas ♪</i>

1:22:39.666 --> 1:22:41.791
<i>♪ On, on they send</i>
<i>On without end ♪</i>

1:22:41.875 --> 1:22:43.375
<i>♪ Their joyful tone</i>
<i>To every home ♪</i>

1:22:43.458 --> 1:22:45.125
<i>What must you have thought of me?</i>

1:22:46.708 --> 1:22:48.666
<i>Well, I assumed you to be a loyal wife.</i>

1:22:49.208 --> 1:22:50.041
<i>[sighs]</i>

1:22:51.291 --> 1:22:52.708
<i>And I returned to my work.</i>

1:22:55.125 --> 1:22:56.250
<i>New York?</i>

1:22:58.916 --> 1:23:00.500
<i>It's been my home for the past</i>

1:23:02.166 --> 1:23:03.083
<i>four years.</i>

1:23:05.791 --> 1:23:06.666
<i>[chuckles]</i>

1:23:11.333 --> 1:23:12.333
<i>I was on my way…</i>

1:23:15.541 --> 1:23:16.625
<i>to meet you.</i>

1:23:24.291 --> 1:23:25.333
<i>There was a crash.</i>

1:23:28.458 --> 1:23:30.166
<i>I was left unconscious.</i>

1:23:32.708 --> 1:23:34.541
<i>I couldn't remember anything.</i>

1:23:36.125 --> 1:23:37.333
<i>Until I saw you tonight.</i>

1:23:37.916 --> 1:23:41.166
<i>I had found your letters,</i>
<i>but I was told you…</i>

1:23:47.375 --> 1:23:50.208
<i>I was misled. I thought that I'd lost you.</i>

1:23:51.666 --> 1:23:55.375
<i>Misplaced, perhaps.</i>

1:23:57.583 --> 1:23:59.208
<i>[softly] But certainly not lost.</i>

1:24:02.458 --> 1:24:03.291
<i>[softly] Boot?</i>

1:24:04.500 --> 1:24:05.666
<i>Yes, dear Jennifer.</i>

1:24:06.291 --> 1:24:07.833
<i>Would you kiss me, please?</i>

1:24:07.916 --> 1:24:10.166
<i>[romantic music playing]</i>

1:24:30.666 --> 1:24:31.583
<i>Come back with me.</i>

1:24:34.958 --> 1:24:36.125
<i>I can't lose you again.</i>

1:24:37.166 --> 1:24:38.625
<i>Too many things have changed.</i>

1:24:42.708 --> 1:24:44.083
<i>I'm still in love with you.</i>

1:24:46.208 --> 1:24:47.875
<i>[softly] Can you please help me?</i>

1:25:04.208 --> 1:25:05.125
<i>I have a daughter.</i>

1:25:13.083 --> 1:25:13.916
<i>What's her name?</i>

1:25:15.166 --> 1:25:16.000
<i>Esme.</i>

1:25:17.541 --> 1:25:18.375
<i>She's two.</i>

1:25:24.750 --> 1:25:25.625
<i>Bring her.</i>

1:25:27.041 --> 1:25:27.875
<i>Hmm?</i>

1:25:35.750 --> 1:25:36.583
<i>I can't.</i>

1:25:39.166 --> 1:25:40.291
<i>Forgive me.</i>

1:25:48.041 --> 1:25:48.875
<i>I'll wait.</i>

1:25:52.250 --> 1:25:54.083
<i>Tell me to wait for you, and I will.</i>

1:25:57.333 --> 1:25:58.166
<i>I love you.</i>

1:26:02.666 --> 1:26:03.500
<i>I always have.</i>

1:26:10.500 --> 1:26:11.416
<i>I'm so sorry.</i>

1:26:24.083 --> 1:26:26.666
<i>[Ellie] So that was the last</i>
<i>you saw of each other?</i>

1:26:29.625 --> 1:26:30.666
<i>No more letters?</i>

1:26:32.708 --> 1:26:33.666
<i>No more letters.</i>

1:26:39.833 --> 1:26:41.166
<i>Do you have them with you?</i>

1:26:41.625 --> 1:26:44.625
<i>Yes. The… the letters, yes.</i>

1:26:45.916 --> 1:26:46.750
<i>Here.</i>

1:26:53.250 --> 1:26:55.875
<i>What if I could put</i>
<i>the two of you in touch?</i>

1:26:58.375 --> 1:26:59.458
<i>No.</i>

1:26:59.541 --> 1:27:04.333
<i>I chose to respect</i>
<i>Jennifer's decision all those years ago.</i>

1:27:05.166 --> 1:27:07.541
<i>It seems only right to me</i>
<i>I continue to do so.</i>

1:27:11.875 --> 1:27:14.458
<i>I wonder if these ought</i>
<i>to be returned to Mrs. Sterling.</i>

1:27:14.541 --> 1:27:15.541
<i>I already tried.</i>

1:27:17.041 --> 1:27:18.875
<i>[O'Hare] Well, you're a journalist.</i>

1:27:22.291 --> 1:27:23.125
<i>Try again.</i>

1:27:23.791 --> 1:27:25.500
<i>[door buzzer buzzes]</i>

1:27:28.500 --> 1:27:32.500
<i>[door buzzer buzzes]</i>

1:27:32.583 --> 1:27:33.708
<i>[woman] Can I help you?</i>

1:27:34.750 --> 1:27:35.583
<i>Um.</i>

1:27:38.375 --> 1:27:39.500
<i>Mrs. Stirling?</i>

1:27:40.041 --> 1:27:40.916
<i>Yes.</i>

1:27:42.375 --> 1:27:46.875
<i>Well, I'm, um… I'm Ellie.</i>
<i>Ellie Haworth from the, uh…</i>

1:27:48.000 --> 1:27:53.708
<i>Um, look, I'm… I'm… I'm just…</i>
<i>I'm not trying to… I just…</i>

1:27:55.000 --> 1:27:58.291
<i>I met with Mr. O'Hare, with Anthony,</i>

1:27:58.375 --> 1:28:01.791
<i>and, um, he wanted me to give you these.</i>

1:28:03.875 --> 1:28:06.625
<i>He wants you to have them,</i>
<i>and it is his express wish.</i>

1:28:11.125 --> 1:28:12.791
<i>[Jenny] What did you two discuss?</i>

1:28:13.375 --> 1:28:15.541
<i>[Ellie] Well, uh, you.</i>

1:28:16.500 --> 1:28:17.333
<i>Mostly.</i>

1:28:20.000 --> 1:28:21.875
<i>He… he told me what happened.</i>

1:28:23.791 --> 1:28:27.333
<i>In the end, you… you chose your family.</i>

1:28:29.791 --> 1:28:31.708
<i>[dramatic instrumental music playing]</i>

1:28:34.166 --> 1:28:36.041
<i>[weeping]</i>

1:28:41.750 --> 1:28:42.625
<i>[sniffles]</i>

1:29:08.000 --> 1:29:11.708
<i>["Johnny Boy" by Melanie playing]</i>

1:29:11.791 --> 1:29:16.583
<i>♪ Johnny boy, my friend</i>
<i>Stop them again ♪</i>

1:29:16.666 --> 1:29:20.791
<i>♪ For a lonely girl</i>
<i>In the world ♪</i>

1:29:20.875 --> 1:29:25.541
<i>♪ Of the stone buildings</i>
<i>That would turn brown ♪</i>

1:29:25.625 --> 1:29:28.000
<i>♪ If they were born ♪</i>

1:29:28.083 --> 1:29:31.458
<i>♪ In the town</i>
<i>Where the trees are grown ♪</i>

1:29:31.541 --> 1:29:38.541
<i>♪ Johnny boy</i>
<i>I'm alone ♪</i>

1:29:39.916 --> 1:29:42.958
<i>♪ Please take me home ♪</i>

1:29:47.583 --> 1:29:49.041
<i>What's all this, then?</i>

1:29:49.125 --> 1:29:53.208
<i>♪ Johnny boy, my friend</i>
<i>Please hold my hand ♪</i>

1:29:53.291 --> 1:29:55.708
<i>-♪ In the middle of the-- ♪</i>
-[record turns off]

1:30:01.833 --> 1:30:02.666
<i>You lied to me.</i>

1:30:05.541 --> 1:30:06.750
<i>You told me he was dead.</i>

1:30:13.166 --> 1:30:14.166
<i>Why?</i>

1:30:19.500 --> 1:30:21.208
<i>For the sake of our marriage.</i>

1:30:22.541 --> 1:30:24.791
<i>By allowing me to believe</i>
<i>that I'd killed him?</i>

1:30:36.250 --> 1:30:41.500
<i>I know that I betrayed you, Lawrence.</i>

1:30:43.708 --> 1:30:45.291
<i>I live with it every day.</i>

1:30:46.833 --> 1:30:51.083
<i>And I have spent</i>
<i>the last four years of my life…</i>

1:30:53.666 --> 1:30:55.416
<i>trying to be a better wife for you.</i>

1:30:57.458 --> 1:31:00.083
<i>But I remember, Larry,</i>
<i>I remember everything.</i>

1:31:01.166 --> 1:31:05.500
<i>And the truth is, you and I were broken</i>
<i>long before Anthony came into my life.</i>

1:31:05.583 --> 1:31:07.166
<i>-[softly] Jennifer.</i>
<i>-Don't touch me.</i>

1:31:07.250 --> 1:31:09.833
<i>-Jenny, listen--</i>
<i>-[sternly] No, you listen to me now!</i>

1:31:12.375 --> 1:31:17.125
<i>[softly] The only reason I am still here</i>
<i>is because of our daughter.</i>

1:31:18.291 --> 1:31:22.125
<i>From this day forward,</i>
<i>I am your wife in name only.</i>

1:31:22.208 --> 1:31:25.291
<i>And if you so much as attempt</i>
<i>to treat me otherwise,</i>

1:31:26.041 --> 1:31:28.958
<i>I will take our daughter,</i>
<i>and I will leave.</i>

1:31:29.041 --> 1:31:30.083
<i>[grabs roughly]</i>

1:31:31.791 --> 1:31:36.041
<i>Now if you think the courts will side with</i>
<i>an adulteress, then you're delusional.</i>

1:31:37.875 --> 1:31:40.791
<i>And if you try to leave,</i>
<i>if you try to take my child,</i>

1:31:40.875 --> 1:31:41.875
<i>I will destroy you,</i>

1:31:42.625 --> 1:31:44.833
<i>and you'll never see her again.</i>
<i>Do you understand?</i>

1:31:46.500 --> 1:31:47.500
<i>[releases roughly]</i>

1:31:54.625 --> 1:31:56.625
<i>[suspenseful instrumental music playing]</i>

1:31:58.375 --> 1:31:59.666
<i>[whispering] Hi, darling.</i>

1:32:00.708 --> 1:32:01.750
<i>Hi, baby.</i>

1:32:02.791 --> 1:32:05.000
<i>We're gonna go on an adventure, okay?</i>

1:32:12.833 --> 1:32:17.000
<i>Hello, I'm looking for Mr. Anthony O'Hare.</i>
<i>He's in room 268.</i>

1:32:17.083 --> 1:32:20.166
<i>[woman] Mr. O'Hare</i>
<i>is no longer staying with us here.</i>

1:32:25.333 --> 1:32:26.625
<i>When did he leave?</i>

1:32:26.708 --> 1:32:27.708
<i>Yesterday.</i>

1:32:31.416 --> 1:32:32.291
<i>Thank you.</i>

1:32:34.000 --> 1:32:36.291
<i>[woman] Ma'am? Stop for a second.</i>

1:32:36.375 --> 1:32:38.875
<i>-Anthony?</i>
<i>-[woman] Excuse me. Ma'am?</i>

1:32:40.041 --> 1:32:41.541
<i>What's going on in here?</i>

1:32:42.000 --> 1:32:43.833
<i>[woman] I've been trying to explain.</i>

1:32:44.500 --> 1:32:46.125
<i>-[man] Mary Ellen?</i>
<i>-[Jenny] Anthony?</i>

1:32:47.458 --> 1:32:51.333
<i>I'm… I'm looking for Anthony O'Hare.</i>
<i>I need to know where he is, please.</i>

1:32:51.416 --> 1:32:54.875
<i>I'm sorry to be the one to tell you this,</i>
<i>but Anthony handed in his notice.</i>

1:32:54.958 --> 1:32:56.708
<i>He resigned this morning.</i>

1:32:56.791 --> 1:33:00.041
<i>-Did he leave a forwarding address?</i>
<i>-I'm sorry to say he did not.</i>

1:33:23.833 --> 1:33:26.250
<i>Perhaps you could see to it</i>
<i>that he gets these.</i>

1:33:26.333 --> 1:33:29.583
<i>If you hear from Anthony again,</i>
<i>please tell him I was looking for him.</i>

1:33:50.708 --> 1:33:53.750
<i>So then you…</i>
<i>you went back to your husband?</i>

1:33:55.750 --> 1:33:57.750
<i>I just couldn't risk losing her.</i>

1:33:59.083 --> 1:34:01.208
<i>And I did eventually leave him,</i>

1:34:02.166 --> 1:34:05.333
<i>when I knew for certain</i>
<i>that the law would support my decision.</i>

1:34:06.250 --> 1:34:07.458
<i>What about Mr. O'Hare?</i>

1:34:08.500 --> 1:34:12.541
<i>Did you try getting in touch</i>
<i>with him once… once you'd left?</i>

1:34:12.625 --> 1:34:17.375
<i>I would scour the papers</i>
<i>every day looking for his name.</i>

1:34:18.791 --> 1:34:21.666
<i>Nothing. And eventually,</i>
<i>I stopped buying the paper.</i>

1:34:21.750 --> 1:34:24.291
<i>It felt to me</i>
<i>as though he didn't want to be found.</i>

1:34:24.958 --> 1:34:26.125
<i>But what about now?</i>

1:34:28.708 --> 1:34:32.666
<i>You know, he doesn't know that</i>
<i>you tried to go after him. He has no idea.</i>

1:34:32.750 --> 1:34:36.083
<i>Probably for the best. We had our chance.</i>

1:34:36.166 --> 1:34:39.875
<i>Yes, but what…</i>
<i>what if you could have another chance?</i>

1:34:39.958 --> 1:34:42.291
<i>Our heart can only take so much,</i>

1:34:42.375 --> 1:34:46.958
<i>and I fear, at my age,</i>
<i>I've reached my limit.</i>

1:34:51.541 --> 1:34:54.541
<i>[Ellie] </i>The past can be intoxicating.
It can draw you in,

1:34:54.625 --> 1:34:57.666
<i>create the illusion</i>
<i>that things were better, you were happier,</i>

1:34:57.750 --> 1:35:00.250
<i>or experiences were richer back then.</i>

1:35:00.916 --> 1:35:02.541
<i>It can also debilitate you,</i>

1:35:02.625 --> 1:35:06.791
<i>leaving you stuck in your memories</i>
<i>of pain, heartbreak, and disappointment,</i>

1:35:06.875 --> 1:35:10.458
<i>holding you back from even attempting</i>
<i>another shot at happiness.</i>

1:35:10.541 --> 1:35:14.291
<i>They say if we don't learn from past</i>
<i>mistakes, we're bound to repeat them.</i>

1:35:14.916 --> 1:35:17.791
<i>But can we also learn</i>
<i>to let go of the past,</i>

1:35:17.875 --> 1:35:20.500
<i>learn to forge ahead,</i>
<i>keeping the knowledge close</i>

1:35:20.583 --> 1:35:24.500
<i>but not letting it overtake</i>
<i>our ability to try again, to feel again?</i>

1:35:24.583 --> 1:35:26.166
<i>Ellie, it's fantastic.</i>

1:35:26.708 --> 1:35:28.250
<i>Okay. Um…</i>

1:35:30.458 --> 1:35:32.625
<i>-[woman] Really good work here.</i>
<i>-[chuckles]</i>

1:35:33.125 --> 1:35:35.583
<i>Well, that's great.</i>
<i>I… I appreciate that.</i>

1:35:37.500 --> 1:35:39.541
<i>[uplifting instrumental music playing]</i>

1:35:41.000 --> 1:35:42.208
<i>I'll be back later.</i>

1:35:51.791 --> 1:35:55.208
<i>[phone ringing]</i>

1:36:00.541 --> 1:36:03.541
<i>-Hello?</i>
<i>-[Ellie] </i>Hi, it's, uh… it's Ellie.

1:36:03.625 --> 1:36:04.875
<i>Um, how's it going?</i>

1:36:05.625 --> 1:36:07.833
<i>Yeah, I'm fine. You?</i>

1:36:08.541 --> 1:36:09.833
<i>[Ellie] </i>Uh, pretty good.

1:36:12.875 --> 1:36:16.166
<i>No, that's… that's…</i>
<i>that's not actually true.</i>

1:36:17.750 --> 1:36:20.125
<i>I don't know why I left</i>
<i>without saying goodbye,</i>

1:36:20.208 --> 1:36:23.083
<i>and I don't know why I didn't reply</i>
<i>to any of your messages. That's, uh…</i>

1:36:23.166 --> 1:36:27.625
<i>That's a really shitty thing, and, I mean,</i>
<i>if you wanted to message me again,</i>

1:36:27.708 --> 1:36:29.583
<i>you have my word you'll get a reply.</i>

1:36:30.583 --> 1:36:36.041
<i>But I get there might be a ton of reasons</i>
<i>why you don't wanna speak to me</i>

1:36:36.125 --> 1:36:38.458
<i>or write to me or hang out with me.</i>

1:36:38.541 --> 1:36:43.500
<i>And, in truth, I'm kinda worried you might</i>
<i>think I'm a pretty heinous individual</i>

1:36:43.583 --> 1:36:44.916
<i>if you get to know me, but…</i>

1:36:47.583 --> 1:36:48.500
<i>But at this point,</i>

1:36:50.625 --> 1:36:53.875
<i>I don't think being afraid to try</i>
<i>is a good enough reason for anything.</i>

1:36:55.625 --> 1:36:56.541
<i>And I…</i>

1:36:57.458 --> 1:36:59.791
<i>I think you're fucking tip-top, Rory.</i>

1:37:00.458 --> 1:37:02.333
<i>And I'd…</i>

1:37:03.541 --> 1:37:05.208
<i>I'd really love to see you again.</i>

1:37:07.791 --> 1:37:10.083
<i>I hope you don't mind</i>
<i>me saying that. [chuckles]</i>

1:37:14.125 --> 1:37:15.333
<i>[sighs]</i>

1:37:15.875 --> 1:37:17.458
<i>Look, where… where are you?</i>

1:37:18.125 --> 1:37:19.791
<i>I'm… I'm… I'm outside.</i>

1:37:21.166 --> 1:37:22.000
<i>Sorry?</i>

1:37:22.666 --> 1:37:24.750
<i>I'm outside your flat. [chuckles]</i>

1:37:27.833 --> 1:37:28.958
<i>Oh my God. That's so creepy.</i>

1:37:29.041 --> 1:37:33.083
<i>Yeah, well, I was aiming for industrious</i>
<i>but I… um, I take your point. [chuckles]</i>

1:37:34.208 --> 1:37:36.083
<i>Okay, okay, wait there. Just keep talking.</i>

1:37:36.166 --> 1:37:38.375
<i>I'm gonna come down. Keep talking.</i>

1:37:38.458 --> 1:37:40.458
<i>[romantic instrumental music playing]</i>

1:37:46.416 --> 1:37:47.458
<i>[Ellie] I'm so sor--</i>

1:38:05.875 --> 1:38:08.291
<i>I found them. Both of them.</i>

1:38:09.958 --> 1:38:11.125
<i>I went to see them. [laughs]</i>

1:38:11.208 --> 1:38:12.416
<i>-You're kidding.</i>
<i>-No.</i>

1:38:13.500 --> 1:38:14.916
<i>Shit. What did they say?</i>

1:38:15.000 --> 1:38:18.000
<i>-She tried everything.</i>
<i>-He still doesn't know she went after him?</i>

1:38:18.083 --> 1:38:19.958
<i>-No, he's got no idea.</i>
<i>-So you have to tell him.</i>

1:38:20.041 --> 1:38:23.250
<i>I know! I want to,</i>
<i>but they don't wanna see each other.</i>

1:38:23.333 --> 1:38:26.500
<i>If that was true, then why keep</i>
<i>the PO box open the whole time?</i>

1:38:27.125 --> 1:38:28.833
<i>That doesn't make any sense.</i>

1:38:30.041 --> 1:38:31.500
<i>That is a really good point.</i>

1:38:34.291 --> 1:38:35.750
<i>She really came after me?</i>

1:38:38.625 --> 1:38:39.708
<i>She said that to you?</i>

1:38:52.791 --> 1:38:54.791
<i>[soft instrumental music playing]</i>

1:39:03.875 --> 1:39:04.750
<i>[O'Hare] </i>Dear J,

1:39:06.750 --> 1:39:09.750
<i>please forgive this brief intrusion, but</i>

1:39:10.750 --> 1:39:12.541
<i>as I'm sure you are aware,</i>

1:39:14.833 --> 1:39:18.166
<i>our very separate lives have thankfully,</i>

1:39:19.541 --> 1:39:21.208
<i>at least for this old man,</i>

1:39:24.583 --> 1:39:26.625
<i>once again intercepted.</i>

1:39:31.166 --> 1:39:32.958
<i>In the intervening years,</i>

1:39:33.958 --> 1:39:38.083
<i>I've thought of you</i>
<i>with a constancy I hesitate to now admit.</i>

1:39:39.833 --> 1:39:40.791
<i>Missing you.</i>

1:39:47.916 --> 1:39:50.708
<i>So I shall venture one last time,</i>

1:39:52.666 --> 1:39:54.333
<i>with some trepidation.</i>

1:39:59.375 --> 1:40:00.583
<i>Postman's Park,</i>

1:40:02.416 --> 1:40:03.250
<i>Friday,</i>

1:40:05.083 --> 1:40:06.166
<i>2:00 p.m.</i>

1:40:09.708 --> 1:40:11.125
<i>Yours respectfully,</i>

1:40:14.458 --> 1:40:15.291
<i>B.</i>

1:40:19.833 --> 1:40:21.166
<i>Oh, she's not coming.</i>

1:40:24.250 --> 1:40:25.166
<i>At least we tried.</i>

1:40:28.541 --> 1:40:29.750
<i>I'll go and get him.</i>

1:40:45.458 --> 1:40:46.291
<i>[sighs]</i>

1:41:31.541 --> 1:41:32.375
<i>[chuckles]</i>

1:41:34.666 --> 1:41:37.916
<i>How about we close our eyes?</i>

1:41:40.416 --> 1:41:41.291
<i>[chuckles]</i>

1:41:52.666 --> 1:41:53.541
<i>A letter.</i>

1:41:55.833 --> 1:41:57.208
<i>An invitation…</i>

1:41:59.833 --> 1:42:00.708
<i>to come away.</i>

1:42:03.958 --> 1:42:05.000
<i>To start again.</i>

1:42:11.708 --> 1:42:12.708
<i>[O'Hare] </i>Marylebone.

1:42:13.750 --> 1:42:14.708
<i>Waiting.</i>

1:42:21.916 --> 1:42:23.166
<i>[whistle blows]</i>

1:42:23.250 --> 1:42:25.625
<i>I am starting to worry now.</i>

1:42:25.708 --> 1:42:26.583
<i>[whistle blows]</i>

1:42:28.041 --> 1:42:29.583
<i>[Jenny] </i>But there's really no need.

1:42:29.666 --> 1:42:31.666
<i>[uplifting instrumental music playing]</i>

1:42:34.458 --> 1:42:36.250
<i>[panting, chuckles]</i>

1:42:37.166 --> 1:42:38.250
<i>Because I'm right here.</i>

1:42:38.333 --> 1:42:39.541
<i>[laughs]</i>

1:42:41.000 --> 1:42:42.166
<i>[softly]</i> Right on time.

1:43:19.916 --> 1:43:22.541
<i>["What'cha Gonna Do About It"</i>
<i>by Doris Troy playing]</i>

1:43:28.500 --> 1:43:31.916
<i>♪ Our love, yeah ♪</i>

1:43:34.416 --> 1:43:38.291
<i>♪ Is slowly going on the rocks now ♪</i>

1:43:38.375 --> 1:43:40.250
<i>♪ Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah ♪</i>

1:43:40.958 --> 1:43:46.791
<i>♪ Tell me, tell me, baby</i>
<i>What'cha gonna do 'bout it ♪</i>

